establish model in industrial innovation
after its competitor invent the front load wash machine , the ceo of the american im company believe that each of its employee have the ability for innovation , and formulate strategic countermeasure for innovation in the industry .
1. establish an innovation fund with a maximum amount of 1,000 u.s. dollar .
2. choose 100 innovative concept to encourage employee to conduct research and development during their work time or spare time .
3. from among them , pick out 50 for submission to an assessment committee to assess .
since the tangshan earthquake , the start point for construction standard in the mainland be that under an earthquake of the same magnitude , building should preserve their basic frame without collapse .
however , most of the building in this hard @-@ hit area do not meet these requirement , with the widespread collapse of school building in particular arouse intense public disgust .
raise standard to in excess of tangshan 's 8.0 magnitude could leave authority with some breathe space for explanation , and alleviate public anger .
accord to information leak from numerous channel , we can say for certain that before the earthquake struck , the serious earthquake risk in the ngawa region be already well know to the ccp .
although current forecast standard cannot give us an accurate prediction of the exact time , place , and strength of an earthquake , there be considerable experience accumulate both in china and overseas in predict to within the timeframe of a month , and the area of a province .
in region where the earthquake risk be high , warn the public and spread disaster prevention awareness could greatly reduce casualty during earthquake ; this be the very minimum duty that any responsible government should undertake .
in the past the ccp have do a lot of these sort of thing , but on this occasion not only do nothing , but in response to query from the public pull out some whop lie , play syntax game with word like " geological disaster " and " earthquake disaster ".
i think that if our earthquake administration have be able beforehand to do a simulation of big earthquake on this longmenshan mountain earthquake belt , then on that day of may 12 , once the earthquake administration have measure the quake at a magnitude of 7.8 , we would have be able to broadly judge the extent of damage and destruction in the earthquake disaster zone .
if the simulation program be well design , circumstance like debris block road , heavy rainfall obstruct parachute drop , power and communication outage should all have be within expectation .
instead in this instance the liberation army headquarters emergency contingency plan obviously be not a contingency plan design with earthquake as the assume condition , as the soldier all rush straight to wenchuan , without immediately send out troop in the direction of badly @-@ hit area beichuan , qingchuan and gansu 's longnan ; only 24 hour later be the full extent of the disaster area take into consideration .
in addition , the breakdown in communication also bring a serious problem to the surface . in the past , red army regiment be able to maintain contact with central headquarters by relying on just one batter radio . on this occasion though , people have no way to deal with the communication failure .
it be clear that preparation prior to the event be not construct on the basis of an earthquake disaster simulation .
while it should have be a disaster relief command that take overall leadership , it have suddenly come face @-@ to @-@ face with the broad base of disaster victim , directly deal with them .
the lack or serious shortage of intermediate layer of party organization and unit between the two have result in its inability to consider major issue with endless minor issue on hand , such that even if it be highly capable , it won't last long , as it will be drag down by numerous petty thing .
this would have be unimaginable during the great tangshan earthquake . a time without volunteer or mental worker , such petty thing as directly deal with average people be perform by the most primary party branch , as well as enterprise and public institution .
as soon as the earthquake occur , grass @-@ root organization contact their own people and average people also contact their own system or department , in an interdependent manner .
under the centralized leadership of higher @-@ level organization , everyone act to make the rescue effort very outstanding and successful , such that the great tangshan earthquake , which happen just a few year ago , be forget all together in the subsequent reform and open @-@ up .
it be obvious that no social or political problem be leave then , nor be sequelae that cause headache to later generation .
during a time of prosperity and happiness , such a big earthquake suddenly struck .
many people die , much property be destroy , it be quite clearly a great disaster .
but it be not totally without benefit , and i believe that its greatest benefit be that it serve to strip off the false benevolence that compose the outer skin of the elitist , the politician , the capitalist , and expose once and for all the rotten cannibalistic core within .
and an additional benefit be that many people who have be delude came to their sense .
temporarily lay aside these abstract thing and avoid speak at length , say only a few detail that leave the elitist , the politician and capitalist highly embarrass .
the expert have just finish say " sacrifice yourself to help others be a foolish idea ", when the leader have no choice but to call once again for selfless devotion .
this be mere chicanery , to the point where before engaging in life @-@ save , donation to charity , these sort of behaviors , an idea have to be flash through people 's mind :
am i be foolish in do this ?
and when people see on cctv those private firm manufacture tent in jiangsu and zhejiang work overtime to produce more tent , the first idea that popped to mind i 'm afraid was probably " this time these capitalist have struck it big ! "
" why be it that these capitalist instead of those capitalist get the big order form , surely there could n't be anything fishy involve ?
