wang shi 's experience of be under public condemnation underscore to a certain extent the tense relationship between the rich and poor class in chinese society ;
because as china grow prosperous day by day , the gap of wealth between the successful elite and the remain 1.3 billion people be widen .
thirty year ago , people have basically the same income , which be all deplorably meager .
however , hurun report ( hurun report ) show that by 2007 , there be a total of 106 billionaires ( in u.s. dollar ) in china , with the number of people only next to that of the unite state .
now , wang shi say , these response have have effect on me .
he admit that he be not sensitive enough to the current situation when he write his blog .
wang shi note additionally that since china currently have not yet establish a sound system of social security insurance , the grow hatred of the rich be unavoidable .
on tuesday , wanke announce that it would make an additional donation of rmb 100 million yuan for the temporary resettlement and post @-@ disaster reconstruction in the next three to five year .
yao ming , the basketball player who be hail as a national hero thank to his success in establish himself in nba , be also blame after he announce his donation of rmb two million yuan because a rumor on the internet allege he have donate one million u.s. dollar for disaster relief of hurricane katrina ( hurricane ) in 2005 .
even so , donation behavior and the treatment of donation behavior should not deviate from two principle , namely that it be voluntary and do not seek return . otherwise , the donation lose its original mean .
in actual fact , whether it be mcdonalds or any other foreign own enterprise in china on the so @-@ call " international iron rooster " blacklist , they all give generously to the cause of help the disaster victim , exhibit their social responsibility .
even if by comparison some company really do n't donate a huge amount , they should not be besiege or subject to verbal violence in the arena of public opinion .
donate , after all , be not a legal obligation that company must carry out . urge business to donate apart from the force of moral consideration should not take the form of any other coercive mean .
as long as a company 's source of income be legal , any compulsory payment outside of legal obligation be a kind of theft .
even in an abnormal circumstance such as disaster relief , legal order and the right bestow upon by law should be respect .
if we be unfortunate enough to be unable to avoid become a disaster victim , we can at least preserve the nobility and dignity of humanity and not turn into rabble .
the lawsuit propose by hai ming do not have a clear subject of the right of action ; moreover it do not satisfy the legal requirement for libel .
for example , he fail to clarify whether cafferty 's comment be an argument over opinion or an act of spread an untruthful statement .
the malicious intent of cafferty have not be establish , either . more importantly , he have be unable to offer anything as to how to establish the damage to the 1.3 billion chinese people .
in addition , in his complaint , it be say that chinese people have already express their displeasure through demonstration .
here it be a country with the freedom of speech .
on the issue of libel , court only support those who have actually suffer damage and have no other way to seek justice .
therefore , it be very hard for the government , politician , and public figure to get legal protection on the issue of libel ,
because they have the capability to clear themselves of " smear ."
if you have already clear your own reputation through legal protest , for example , chinese people be not goon and thug , then a lawsuit be meaningless .
remember , a lawsuit for libel be only to clear your name and get compensation .
