for example , the value of " seize the pleasure of the moment " also have a long history .
" sing a song when thou have wine , seize the day since life be short." some people in contemporary time think we should " satisfy and die ."
some people have go so far on the road that they " don't know how to eat or play , "
and other take nude picture and flaunt them online .
for another example , the pursuit of office title and level can also be trace back to the old day .
in ancient time there be zhou li to distinguish the order of hierarchy and nobility , construct a pyramid @-@ like social organizational structure .
the son of the heaven wore different clothe than others . the color of a door and the number of caldrons use for meal be all symbol to distinguish the hierarchy and nobility of people .
the aim be to settle dispute , stop fight and stabilize the society .
however , simultaneously it have also establish a system that value life accord to office level , which to the contrary trigger contention and destabilized the society .
yet no matter how many change of dynasty there be , the value system have always be carry on .
higher or lower rank in qing dynasty be distinguish by bird and animal pattern on clothe , taiping heavenly kingdom use the size and color of a sedan chair as the symbol to distinguish between different rank , and modern people use the motor vehicle displacement as a symbol to distinguish between different position , all of which can be trace to the same origin .
