when forecast earthquake , why do it happen that only a few case be successful while most case be failure ?
accord to this writer 's many year of research on precursory sign , the existence of precursory sign and earthquake prediction be two issue that be both connect and mutual differentiate .
the appearance of a precursory sign do n't mean it can accurately forecast the three element of an earthquake , because precursory sign be extremely complicate .
there be certain difference in the category , breadth , distribution range , and duration of precursory sign of different type of earthquake in different place .
in " regional nature of precursory sign of earthquake , " this writer divide earthquake into two major type accord to the overall characteristic of pre @-@ earthquake sign : strike @-@ type and slip @-@ type earthquake .
the former occur in area where internal fault block or fault line converge but not intersect , while the latter occur in active fault line .
strike @-@ type earthquake have various type of precursory sign , which be widespread , long @-@ last , and quite variable .
slip @-@ type earthquake have fewer type of precursory sign , which have a smaller distribution range , short duration period , and smaller range of change .
in chengdu , which be over 100 kms away from the epicenter , the earthquake should not have an intensity of over 7 , or 8 at the most .
there should not be any safety problem for class a building like those at the airport , hospital and school that be design to withstand a intensity of 8 .
so most building in chengdu should still be able to use after emergency assessment , and citizen may go home reassure .
if not so , an investigation should be conduct for any jerry @-@ build project .
if large sum of money have be spend to provide protection , yet it fail to work when the earthquake come ,
such that nobody dare to live at home , be able to use hospital , or accesses airport , then have the money be throw for nothing ?
probably some would say the national build criteria for earthquake resistance be enact in recent year , and older building may not comply with the requirement .
however , at the same time the government enact the earthquake resistance criteria , it require all exist building which do not satisfy the criteria to be reinforce and remove of danger in a timely fashion .
thus one cannot shirk responsibility on excuse that it be an old build .
in addition , the government also have criteria for earthquake resistance and prevention for rural building .
the earthquake in sichuan stun everyone .
elementary school building collapse , and children be bury in the rubble .
middle school building collapse , and young student be bury under the crumble wall .
kindergarten building also collapse , and little child 's frail body fall helplessly next to the crumbled wall where they close their innocent eye forever .
we could n't help cry at this sorrowful scene .
children be the flower of our motherland and future of our motherland .
these flower of life die early in a natural disaster .
natural disaster cannot be predict , but the school building should not have collapse .
why be the building behind the school building still there while the school building where children study collapse from the first floor to the fourth floor leave only crumble wall ?
children , you should n't have depart like this .
every year , all level of people 's congress be hold from local government to the central government .
deputy to the people 's congress , please make an all @-@ around inspection of school building in all area and inspect whether or not the school building in your constituency be up to local earthquake @-@ resistance standard , and then quickly make a proposal accord to the exist problem and push each level of the government to complete rectification and improvement within a limited time .
special legislation in the national people 's congress on construction of school building should be propose .
there need to be special legal procedure for the design , material , construction , completion , and inspection of the school building to ensure that top priority be give to quality and durability .
allow all children to study safely be the sacred and bounden duty of the people 's congress .
in june 1976 , 83 year @-@ old mao zedong have already be revive once after suffer a myocardial infarction .
to get effective care for his condition , the stand committee of the political bureau of the ccp establish a special treatment team , in charge of his medical treatment and care .
the political bureau also specifically assign people to the task of mao zedong 's medical care , take turn with the doctor and nurse to be on constant vigil at his live quarter .
on the day of the tangshan earthquake , i.e. july 28 th , those on duty at mao zedong 's quarter be wang dongxing , wang hongwen , and mao zedong 's confidential secretary , zhang yufeng .
in the early hour of the morning , with the clock hand point to 3 @:@ 42 , the ground of zhongnanhai suddenly start to shudder .
in mao zedong 's residence , the glass window in the foyer door rattle uncontrollably , and there be a huge bang from below like a tractor start up , with mao zedong 's sickbed shake non @-@ stop.......
while mao zedong be convalesce , the employee and medical staff around him be all in a state of high tension , maintain extremely silent surroundings and atmosphere .
in normal time , apart from the talk and noise of medical instrument when the doctor revive him , not a whisper could be hear .
after the ninety , state @-@ own engineer enterprise stop recruit construction worker .
but that be n't to say they stop hire people , but those they take in be all graduate with professional diploma from polytechnic school , technical college , and university ; these staff all went into management .
during the early ninety , the formal employee of this enterprise still have complete work team , such as bricklaying team , woodwork team , steel reinforcement team , and machinery maintenance team , but since they could not cope with a large volume of project task , they be already cooperate with some migrant worker unit , in other word the familiar " contract gang ".
a collision occur between tradition and reality .
due to formal work unit no long take on young employee , work unit get increasingly older and break up .
some staff ( extremely few ) enter management .
a few exceptional former team leader gradually become project manager .
others become material officer , safety officer and quality control officer , etc.
those without connection become staff monitor the construction site------similar to the security guard of today .
the worker no long form complete operate team .
and at this time , migrant worker unit gain an opportunity to develop .
the entire on @-@ site operation work be all carry out by contract gang .
work unit disband .
the status of these worker be also change .
the corrupt mentality that treat dinner and gift @-@ give be necessary for get thing done be deeply root in the mind of people from all walk of society .
in each case of corruption , those power @-@ wield bureaucrat , those scholar or technician who have corner the market in their field , those capitalist with vast wealth , they be the rule force of this society , and also the one who profit from the corruption .
the powerless , pennyless work public with no access to information technology resource %pw be the one who lose out from the corruption .
today 's society be corrupt in every direction , and the direct cause be the reinstatement of private ownership and the scrap of the public supervision of the mao zedong era .
