gang ringleader use cash to have the media make them out as hero ,
capitalist try to annex state @-@ own property team up with scholar and academically demonstrate state @-@ own monopoly to be the reason behind corruption , and then reap in the profit .
frequently the public , under the guidance of the mainstream media , only concern themselves with administrative and judicial corruption ; this in itself be a type of corruption .
do commodity price have a base value worth talk about ?
do commodity have a true value ?
these be already element of uncertainty .
with thing , less be more ; sell as much as you want , as long as somebody will buy .
in fact , in a socialist country one cannot act in that way .
in the area of profit from commodity , there have be no system in place and no legal provision ever since the reform , there be no last word on how many multiple of cost profit be allow to be , or what percentage .
china 's self @-@ sufficient , natural economy be not without any advantage . at least it do n't try to reap large profit off its own people ,
now the exact opposite be the case .
a home appliance - whether you be chinese or a foreigner , which regional category you fit in , whether you be a big city or a small city , whether you be a worker or a peasant - be always the same price .
not know how much profit be in there , not care who can afford it and who can n't , these do not seem to be the principle of socialism .
and with farmer ' grain and rural product , if the country do n't wipe out agricultural tax and do n't offer any subsidy , keep on produce be a problem .
in order to improve the people 's live standard , the government set thing so that grain be always the same price whether sell to big city or to rich people .
with this kind of ratio in existence , in struggle area try for a comfortable life be very difficult .
this issue should attract the close attention of economist .
december 26 , 1975 , mao zedong have his 82 th birth day , his last one .
upon turn 80 , mao zedong feel apparently that he be old and would die soon .
therefore , around his birthday those few year , mao zedong have always talk about life and death from time to time .
one thing he often say be : " 73 and 84 be age at which you will be go even if the king of hell do n't call you ."
also since he turn 80 , people have be pay more and more attention to mao zedong 's birthday .
within the country , people dare not celebrate his birthday publicly , so they would celebrate quietly at home .
local government dare not present gift to mao zedong , but would convey their blessing to mao zedong in various way .
in the year before mao zedong pass away , his hometown hunan would specially send thing like long life noodle on december 26 every year .
for this , mao zedong have accept with pleasure , which be quite unusual .
