since last september , when his daughter be diagnose with symptom such as bloody feces and kidney stone , zhou jin have be in succession to yongzhou in hunan , hebei , xiamen , beijing , guangzhou , and more to take his daughter to hospital for treatment , but the child 's illness have continue to improve and decline .
this september , zhou jin , work in shenzhen , take his daughter to the shenzhen children 's hospital for examination and treatment .
the result of the examination be that the upper rectum be severely infect and the right kidney expand . the kidney stone find in previous hospital treatment be not find this time .
zhou jin say that his daughter , a little over two year old this year , have eat sanlu milk powder for over a year . last september after the bloody feces appear , family member take his daughter to the yongzhou hospital for examination . the doctor inform them that " there be no better treatment method , just have her drink more water ."
worry about his daughter 's illness , zhou jin ask the county hospital to issue a certificate to transfer her to another hospital , to let his daughter go to a better hospital for treatment .
the hospital medical administration department tell zhou jin that issue of the certificate to transfer to another hospital would require the approval of the ministry of health , and more than one month would be need .
" i go repeatedly to find the relevant health department , but they pass my case back and forth . i be helpless and could only take my daughter to the place where i work -- xiamen , to carry out treatment ."
have to suffer this pain .
the doctor in charge tell us that the kid would be out of danger if he could just urinate .
get him to urinate could n't be more difficult !
this urine be more valuable than gold .
he do n't pee at all during the first two or three day in hospital .
we be all desperate at that time .
the hospital already arrange for him to undergo dialysis surgery .
and my satisfy son finally urinate .
out of danger at last , but one trouble pass and another one took its place , there come an acute diarrhea and fever , he be stooling several dozen time every day , you can imagine the suffer .
he have just dance a circle around the grim reaper , and encounted this problem on top of that . i be really worry he would n't pull through .
i do n't know what be happen with the injection treatment at the hospital - the more they inject him the worse the diarrhea , nothing would stop it .
after a few more day of treatment , the kid 's diarrhea be a little better and the doctor get him to do an ultrasound .
the kidney stone have be wash out by the medicine . there be no more stone on his kidney .
the hospitalization be very expensive and our family could n't afford it , so we have no choice but to leave the hospital and go home .
on the night of dragon boat festival he pass out a stone by himself , it be a sedimentary one .
the whole family be really excite , we all think he be better , that he be cure .
