jianguo be not one of these . he work for seven year in a rural part of inner mongolia , become a village head , and be very popular with the local .
he be a dab hand at work the field , and could match the local when it come to drink spirit .
he marry an old school friend of his from beijing , and she stay behind for him , the two live their own little life together in the country .
