the chinese defense budget for 2012 be rmb 670.274 billion , increase by rmb 67.604 billion and 11.2 % compare to the previous year 's estimate budgetary expenditure .
the chinese military expenditure be increase too fast for america , and the increase be currently over rmb 100 billion , but what on earth can china do with this additional amount of more than rmb 100 billion dollar ?
based on the current exchange rate between the renminbi and us dollar , it amount to more than us $ 10 billion , which can purchase more than a hundred of the latest 3.5 generation western fighter plane .
if it be use to manufacture chinese j @-@ 10 fighter , over two hundred plane can be produce , or perhaps even more . in one go , china can improve its prowess in the air by a margin even greater than the total sum of a mid @-@ size western country .
in fact , what america really fear be not the increase of military expenditure , but rather the rapid rate at which china be upgrade its military technology , which may enable china to overtake america soon .
compare to america , china have many inadequacy , for instance , its high technology development be not as mature as america 's , and its basic infrastructure , the standard of education of its citizen , development of its system and so on be also lack . however , china have its own natural advantage , and that be china possess a long history and stability of culture .
some people point out in their comment that this be a serious disadvantage to china when compare to america , as they say that china be carry too heavy a burden which will hinder rapid development ,
in fact , this reason be extremely incorrect , the chinese culture be profound , so whatever problem the country may face , it can draw on its historic experience ,
for instance , when china deal with international affair , it can learn from how the yuan dynasty handle foreign trade and the problem of co @-@ existence between multiple ethnic group , or it could at least draw a lesson from the negative experience .
currently america be drastically cut down on its military expenditure , however it fear that china will substantially increase its military expenditure . america be desperately attempt to return to the pacific ocean as it wish to continue to contain the growth of chinese military strength ,
america control the strait of malacca , and a large majority of china 's ship vessel be under its control . however if america wish to maintain the development of world trade order , its expense will naturally be enormous .
if it be not for the financial crisis , a number of western country have state that they would not have consider budgetary issue for american military deployment .
as a matter of fact , neighboring country need not be too sensitive to the sharp increase in chinese military spend . they fear that china will pose a direct threat to them , but chinese history have show that china have never have the habit of wield its military might to challenge western country , but as for how they habitually view china will depend on the profound influence of the chinese culture .
china do not like to show off , prefer to restrain itself , and the same be true in the field of military matter .
up to now , china reveal that it have three model of the 4 th generation stealth fighter plane under research and development , and the j20 be expect to enter mass production and service next year , which be a direct blow to america ,
however , what be even more terrify for america be that this chinese fighter plane model have already display surprisingly advance performance during combat , and it be fear that its level of technological advancement cannot be match by the f22. after all , this model of fighter plane have never participate in actual inspection up to this point .
perhaps this be understandable for china , but it be inevitable that the 4 th generation chinese fighter plane would create a stir .
the original order have be disrupt . after all , the chinese fighter be no less powerful than the american one .
accord to american media report , china 's military expenditure be expect to reach us $ 200 billion in two year ' time ,
of course there be a strong possibility that this number have be greatly exaggerate , and it be also embellish by the china threat theory . however , such move by america no longer have much effect on china , even if the chinese defense expenditure reach us $ 200 billion , america cannot do anything to china ,
recently , china adopt an aggressive stance , cast negative vote on the syria issue three time , and in relation to japan 's name of the diaoyu island , beijing appear to be send a message that ' we have accumulate sufficient power , and we be not afraid of your distortion of the truth .'
