the status of china as a major world power have begin to be more prominent , and in deal with and direct international affair , china have play an ever more important role .
china 's rapid growth and rise have gradually threaten and challenge the hegemonic position of imperialist america .
this make imperialist america restless , and it have devise every possible mean to contain and check china 's development .
imperialist america want to upset and restrain china with its military sale to taiwan and the taiwan issue !
the taiwan issue have become an everlasting sorrow in the heart of all descendant of china .
imperialist america want to control the middle east and suppress syria and iran mainly because it covet the important strategic location and abundant resource of the middle east .
imperialist america want to overthrow the bashar regime to get rid of the polar bear 's only military base in the middle east ! it do not want the influence of the polar bear to exist in the middle east region over the long term .
imperialist america want to topple iran mainly to take on china , to control china 's resource and contain china 's development .
in addition , it also want to suppress the polar bear and squeeze the live space of china and russia .
in today 's world , the only country that can constitute a threat to the hegemonic position of imperialist america be china and , to a lesser degree , the polar bear .
imperialist america have have far @-@ reach strategic foresight , and each step it take serve to consolidate its hegemony .
imperialist america be suppress china in an all @-@ round way , and we can see imperialist america 's meddle presence in the economy , politics and military affair .
imperialist america have be support little japan , india , the philippine servant and the vietnamese monkey , disturbing the stable environment around china to disrupt the peaceful development and rise of china .
