imperialist america take china as its prime rival and enemy , give up your fantasy that you can make friend with the enemy !
the best method be to make good use of our time to step up our own defense and military construction , cast away all the illusion , and get ready for war !
our ancestor wisely say , " harbor no ill intention against others , but never relax one 's vigilance "!
this be the necessary psychology for get along with friend , but at this moment imperialist america be our enemy stare like a tiger watch its prey , make it more necessary for us to remain vigilant at this time !
china have make a lot of sacrifice to improve its relation with imperialist america , and china have all along tried to become friend with imperialist america ,
although china now need a peaceful and stable environment for its development , we can n't make continual investment without any return .
can sino @-@ american relation be improve ? is friendly development possible ? the key question lie with imperialist america , not china .
imperialist america have always hold the initiative in the development of sino @-@ american relation .
in fact , it be not difficult for china and america to become friend , because china and america , despite their ideological difference , have no land or territorial dispute .
though china and america have fight each other on the battlefield , the war be not directly between china and america .
if imperialist america sincerely want to make friend with china , it must display its sincerity and let the chinese people see actual action and result .
for china , the greatest interest concern imperialist america lie in the taiwan issue .
if imperialist america can stop its military sale to taiwan , provide no support to taiwan , and ensure peace across the taiwan strait , it will allow china to accomplish its great cause of national reunification .
if it refrain from meddle in china 's internal human right issue , and also do not intervene in other affair such as tibet , i believe that china will also sacrifice its other interest to reciprocate the good faith of imperialist america !
only if imperialist america do this can china and america truly become friend and co @-@ exist peacefully as friend from generation to generation .
will imperialist america give up taiwan ? absolutely not !
be use to be a hegemon , imperialist america like to intervene in the internal affair and human right affair of other country , and taiwan be the best chess piece for contain china , so i believe imperialist america will not easily let go of it !
there be even less possibility that it will tolerate a chinese challenge to its position as the world hegemon !
in the year to come , instead of become friend , china and america will only become rival and even enemy !
therefore , it 's unnecessary to harbor any fantasy about imperialist america , china should fundamentally change its mentality , there be no need to fear imperialist america , and we should be ready for a military confrontation with imperialist america at any time .
let 's win the respect of imperialist america and the whole world with our strength .
a peaceful rise be only our unilateral notion , because the big power of the world will not accept the appearance of a powerful china .
only baptize by war can china really become a world power .
the chinese should be ever vigilant and not be deceive by the present peace , active war preparation be the only right choice ,
only when our defense and military have become strong , will we be able to eradicate all aggressor , and only through the baptism of war can china become a truly powerful country .
in my personal opinion , there must be a war between china and america in the future !
what china need to do be to cast away its illusion and get ready for war .
