a pack of luxury cigarette range from as little as a few ten of yuan to more than a hundred yuan , if you smoke a stick , you be puff away one month 's salary for an ordinary worker .
if it be buy with public fund , it may be say that what they be smoke be not cigarette but the " blood and sweat " of the taxpayers .
npc representative ma wenfang propose that consumption of tobacco product on public expense should be universally ban .
there be of course many reason as to why we lag far behind in meet our tobacco control objective .
but one of the undisputable reason be that a huge smoker 's group exist within our huge contingent of civil servant .
among this legion of smoker , a considerable number smoke " free cigarette " which they do n't have to buy with their own money , as they be receive as gift or buy with public fund .
it be precisely because they be not use their own money that they usually smoke luxury cigarette which be unaffordable for most people .
their track performance for blow smoke ring also have a compound effect in repeatedly set new record for consumption expense by civil servant , and it have become an organic portion of officialdom corruption as a whole .
it be precisely this horrify social backdrop that prompt npc representative ma wenfang to solemnly set forth her proposal that consumption of tobacco product on public fund be universally ban .
in our country , there be many civil servant who think their family name be " gong " and such that every expense incur by them , regardless of whether it be for public or private purpose , should be bear by the public . therefore , consumption on public expense can involve almost everything imaginable .
for instance , besides luxury cigarette , other example include luxury liquor , fine wining and dine , luxury car , and overseas tour , and whatever luxury enjoyment and extravagant entertainment they can imagine , they would want to have them all and enjoy them to full , use public fund to settle the bill in full .
if the supreme authority have to draw up separate regulatory document to address every single item for consumption on public expense for nationwide circulation in order to check such extravagance , the mountain of document will really extend towards the sky .
in fact , all that need to be do be to clearly include tobacco product within the anti @-@ corruption regulation ' relevant clause for prohibition of consumption on public fund , and it will suffice .
as for the remain issue , we must ensure that the order and prohibition be fully enforce . if any civil servant dare to violate the law , he will be severely punish accord to the law and regulation .
if this be really carry out in all locality at every level , there would be no cause to worry that the corrupt practice of consumption on public expense , include smoke on public fund , cannot be curb .
