what delight them be that they have an opportunity to report their problem to senior leader and have them take seriously by them , and what worry them be that there be 13 people in the inspection group , come for 20 day or so , and the entertainment expense , the cost of the gift , and the inspection fee and various other item of expenditure would altogether come to 801,900 yuan .
