when i look back to all these year , the urban construction in beijing have experience rapid development .
some people say that it borrow the easterly wind of the olympics . however , i think otherwise .
even though the 2008 olympics allow beijing to display its charisma in front of camera of all caliber that frocked in from all side ,
it have almost be four year since the olympics and the urban development in beijing still have not stop .
speak of urban development , the most representative one be none other than the beijing subway .
those who be born and raise in beijing in the 80 s can almost be call the generation who grow up sit on the subway .
the public transportation then could not be consider as convenient compare to now . bus could hardly be say as provide easy access to all direction .
however , with their extensive coverage , the two subway line provide novelty and convenience to many beijing resident and visitor who travel from afar .
the subway be a distinguish traffic feature of beijing . as one of the first chinese city to have underground transportation , the emergence of subway have provide everyone more choice .
this underground railway line that run through eastern and western beijing have become beijing 's symbol of alternative culture .
day by day , beijing be develop , so be its public transport and highway . eventually , it will usher in the alarm data of 5 million car in 2012 .
meanwhile , the crowd highway and complicate road traffic cause people to have greater expectation in the development of the subway .
i have to applaud the continuous increase in the effort in subway construction of beijing in all these year when i talk about subway development .
in july 2001 , with the success in the bid to host the olympics , beijing subway line 13 also usher in the completion of the entire line and become the newest member of the beijing subway family .
meanwhile , in october 2007 , the closely watch subway line 5 go into operation . it become the new trunk that link southern and northern beijing and intersect with line 1 .
while beijing resident enjoy the modernization of subway line 5 , in july 2008 , the first phase of construction of subway line 10 and in september 2009 , subway line 4 and line 8 all became operational one after another . at the same time , all suburban district and county be all connect by the subway successively .
in about 10 year time , the beijing subway transform from an underground supplementary mean of transport that only have two line to a 15 @-@ line underground transportation network that cover almost the entire beijing from changping in the north to daxing in the south , mentougou in the west , and tongzhou district in the east .
such rapid development be almost unimaginable by anyone and unachievable by any country .
while 2012 be quickly approach , there be even the spectacular scene of four line open at the same time . it be veritably " put all firepower into operation "!
the rapid coverage of underground transportation have bring along prosperity to surround community of the subway . resident no long have to worry about which bus route to take when they go out .
more resident gladly choose to travel by subway . it be both convenient and cozy .
needless to say , the subway have bring about convenience to the travel and work of the resident . more commendable be that the convenient subway have allow more resident to give up their car and choose such green mean of transportation that be environmental friendly .
not only do a reduction in car on the road alleviate traffic pressure on the road ; it also reduce the pressure of air pollution so that more resident can cheer for the blue sky of beijing from their heart .
these be all contribution of the subway . yet , where do the contribution of the subway come from ? they be naturally from the rapid development of the subway in beijing within these 10 year .
the development of the subway be the same as the rapid global development of the city of beijing , it will become a permanent city symbol of beijing and a benefit project that earn the satisfaction of the resident and the respect of the world .
