a letter from the victim 's family
first of all , i would like to thank a kind @-@ hearted person for call the police immediately . i would also like to thank the public security authority for the prompt capture of the perpetrator .
early in the morning on september 1 , my father , as usual , be ride his bicycle to gucheng park for exercise . at jiuli street , he see someone lie on the side of the road , and so , out of kindness , he go up to check up on him and ask him to go home soon . then , three people run up to him , kick and beaing him ( accord to the police , they have drunk four case of beer at the time ) . as a result , my father 's skull suffer serious injury . he bleed profusely and lose consciousness . by the time he be take to the hospital , his pupil be already dilate . however , with prompt rescue give by a doctor , he survive . as there be serious bleed , the doctor perform a life @-@ save surgery to cut off a piece of skull from my father 's head to remove blood clot . due to profuse bleed , some of the blood have already flow into the brainstem and bottom of the brain , put his life in danger .
right now , my father be in very serious condition . on september 1 , he undergo a 5 @-@ hour craniotomy . on september 2 , he have a tracheotomy and a respirator be use to help him breathe . currently , he be still unconscious . after these few day of hospital treatment , he be sometimes able to move his arm and foot , and he be show sign of recovery .
as his children , we feel very terrible now . it have be six day since the incident . under the police 's advice , the perpetrator finally give 10,000 yuan . we have already deliver the money to the hospital . now , almost 50,000 yuan have be spend on the medical bill . we do n't know when we can get money to pay for future medical bill .
we have now already receive a payment reminder from the hospital . if we do not pay on time , the hospital will stop supply medication . when that happen , i cannot bear to think of what will happen to my father .
our family have very poor live condition . my mother only get a minimum welfare pay of 380 yuan , and she have diabetes . my father be a retire coke plant worker . his pay be also just a bit over 1,000 yuan . i be do odd job at a factory , and i have not even make any medical insurance or pension contribution . my elder sister be also an odd @-@ job worker . she have also not make any pension or medical insurance contribution . furthermore , i be go to be a father soon . i have a very heavy family burden . our family now can only rely on my father 's pay to survive . we absolutely cannot afford such high hospital cost .
it have be six day since the incident . as victim , we have the right of a citizen to know some thing :
1. where be the perpetrator from ? how be their family and financial condition ?
2. when can the case be submit to the procuratorate ? when can public prosecution be initiate ?
3. we hope the perpetrator can cooperate actively and take practical action to work together to first save my father 's life .
4. we request to meet the parent of the perpetrator .
we hope the news media can help us to jointly save the life of my kind @-@ hearted father .
we also ask the government department to coordinate with one another and be flexible to activate my father 's medical insurance card and save his life .
after the court verdict be out , all medical cost will be pay back to the medical insurance bureau .
a million thank to the city resident and media for the concern they have show us in this incident . may all you kind @-@ hearted people have a life of peace !
