would everyone agree with illegal construction of high @-@ rise building ?
now , in the hometown of our beloved general secretary hu , such a strange thing be happen .
here be the thing : shenzhen maoye developer have come to hail district , taizhou city , jiangsu province for urban construction , and be welcome by our people .
we do not oppose the construction of high @-@ rise building . however , the developer be go to construct a high @-@ rise build against the law . that be what we be resolutely oppose to !
maoye developer have plan a high @-@ rise build of 150 m in the julangchao lot of the old east station , hail district , taizhou city .
julangchao use to be the eastern suburb park , for which many of the old taizhou people have great affection .
pengxinlidu build no. 14 be just locate at the back of the julangchao lot , and now pengxinlidu build no. 14 be only about 100 meter from the external wall of the original building at the farthest end of the julangchao lot .
how do the developer meet the national requirement for build setback based on a minimum sunshine space of 1 @:@ 1.4 in taizhou ?
aside from the other sunshine shelter , how can the developer ensure a minimum three hour of sunshine on the day of great cold ?
it be certainly not feasible if they want to cheat about the 3 hour technically ,
the plain fact be just in front of us . moreover , be those few entity the only one capable of do sunshine analysis in china ?
we certainly will verify it . a lie will never become the truth !
if the developer can not even give us owner a minimum of three hour on the day of great cold in accordance with the national requirement , which have ensure its best interest , how can it give a reasonable and fair explanation to the society , the vast community of netizens and the mass ?
where be the conscience and moral of the developer ?
we understand that the developer want to get more benefit , but those be suppose to be legitimate benefit !
on the one hand , such act , if illegally infringe upon other people 's interest , will be detrimental to the reputation and long @-@ term future development of the entire maoye group . on the other hand , be people whose interest be infringe all fool ?
will they just let the infringement occur ?
the minimum 3 hour be already difficult to accept . if it be basically an illegal act that make the fundamental three hour even less , think about it - how will thing evolve ?
finally , the contradiction be bind to intensify , make the situation out of hand .
we hope that the developer can seriously think about this issue , avoid loss and seek its own legal interest through rational development and reasonable development accord to law !
if the developer be determine to infringe on our right and interest , we will surely unite as one to defend our legitimate right and interest !
the most strange thing be that some people of high rank even agree with the illegal construction of high @-@ rise building . we hereby earnestly request the people of high rank who agree with the illegal construction of high @-@ rise building to raise their hand and give us a way out !
all netizens and media be welcome to look into this matter . let 's see whether it will ultimately be " power over law " or " law over power " for the official in general secretary hu 's hometown when deal with matter concern a big developer !
all netizens be welcome to look into this matter !
