previously , due to issue about the high @-@ rise building on maoye 's pre @-@ sale rendering and eia by the taizhou municipal environmental protection bureau , the young and old of pengxinlidu build no. 14 be neither sleep nor eat well . some be depress , and some be irritate . in short , we feel very angry .
