the coup in central asia have not succeed . otherwise , once the ring of encirclement be complete , the northern land will cause a headache to you just as the east china sea and the south china sea .
do you still believe that china can become a friend of the us as long as it change its ideology and system ?
the reason for china to ally with russia be that both russia and china need to heal their wound from after the disintegration of the soviet union and with the savage hegemony of the us .
