the reason be simple . russia be a european country . the far east be not its focus , while the us be a country in the asia @-@ pacific region .
do you know the theory of sea control ? nowadays , be there more influence from the us or russia in the issue of the taiwan strait and the south china sea and the far east ? it be the us ! this be clear proof !
do you think that territorial water be n't territory ? in modern time , the strategic and economic value of territorial water be much more than those of land territory . one can only become a strong power and have a say in the international community by control the sea .
why be it not china , its neighbor , but instead great britain , separate by vast ocean , that make india into a colony ?
