even if russia put a little bit more energy into the issue of china and the far east , can it ignore the affair in europe ?
moreover , we would rather say that russia have avail itself of opportunity , than to say that it have invade and occupy china 's territory .
at that time , those place be far away from china 's traditional live area . china 's exploration be a little bit later at that time . there have be few inhabitant around those place in history .
at that time , those place be bitterly cold place cover with waist @-@ deep snow . so we pay no heed to them .
