just like today 's ocean . from the perspective of today , they have huge economic value , so territorial water be also important territory .
however , in the past , they be not discover . and territorial water be not regard as territory . they even exercise trade prohibition on the sea area and close the coastline .
yet the russians avail themselves of a favorable geological location to occupy those place ahead of us . the russians be just avail themselves of opportunity .
at that time , it be a time when big power establish colony everywhere . unlike today , when the behavior of all country be bound by international law .
other big power have to capture colony by war . for example , it be through war that britain and japan occupy hong kong and taiwan respectively .
however , the russians get such a big place without much effort . that be because the ruler of china do n't care for the unexplored place .
they just avail themselves of opportunity . thing such as territory be hard to talk about .
