the earliest to settle here be this world 's largest outdoor seat bronze buddha .
in chinese buddhism , there be five direction - east , west , south , north , and center - and five buddhas .
therefore , hong kong 's tian tan giant buddha at the most southern tip of china , together with lingshan giant buddha in the east , leshan giant buddha in the west , yungang giant buddha in the north , and longmen giant buddha in the central plain , exist as the representative buddhas for each of the five direction of china .
as a result , this place have become holy land in the heart of male and female devotee .
however , to common tourist , more of what this place bring them be wonder and awe .
