i think all we need to do be think of some teacher we have have to know this .
and at the same time i think we can all think of great teacher who have not have a piece of paper from a teacher train college .
with this notion of qualification there be an unholy alliance of two group of people .
the first be the well intend sponsor who think enforce such rule will improve education by keep so call unqualified teacher out .
