it have be note that there have be a lot of thread create on the topic of global warm .
a great number of these topic rapidly descend into bicker and other rule violation .
although one of the biggest thread be put on moderate status , it seem that many of the other thread have spring up in order to avoid moderate status .
that thread have now be close .
since many of the thread cover the same or similar ground , we 've decide to keep only this thread for general global warm discussion , which will be moderate .
unless the topic be very different from the " general " discussion , new thread and post about global warm will be move to that thread if they satisfy the membership agreement .
failure to confine general discussion to this moderate thread or start other thread for general discussion will be treat as rule 6 violation and subject to a series of escalate penalty just like any other membership violation .
we hope this will encourage civility in the discussion of global warm .
we realize this topic inspire strong emotion , but please contain your emotion to those form which be permissible under the membership agreement .
