leader of afghanistan 's interim government hamid karzai say the fight against poppy harvest and the lucrative traffic of opium and heroin will be a top priority .
the anti @-@ drug effort be strongly support by western country , whose population be a major market for heroin and opium from afghanistan .
february 28 , 2002 kabul official announce that afghan police be create their first anti @-@ narcotic unit with the help of the unite nation due to concern that the country could again become a major producer of opium .
february 28 , 2002 qanooni state in talk with russian interior minister boris gryzlov that afghanistan 's main task be to prevent future drug production .
qanooni outline a three @-@ stage plan of action --
afghan authority will seek to ban poppy harvest .
afghan authority will strengthen the border around afghanistan .
afghan authority will cooperate with the security force of neighboring state .
afghanistan be think to be responsible for 75 percent of the world 's opium and 80 percent of the heroin trade illegally in europe .
approximately 11000 russian guard patrol the 1200 @-@ kilometre ( 750 @-@ mile ) border between russia and afghanistan under a 1992 agreement sign by moscow and dushanbe .
the northern alliance oppose the taliban but tolerate the harvest of poppy in territory it control .
afghanistan 's interim government have be in power for 2 month .
