it make it more symbolic and indicate the willingness of those directly involve to eliminate the opium .
the destruction form part of the central committee for drug abuse control 's project new destiny .
it aim to prevent poppy cultivation by distribute seed for substitution crop .
farmer have be ask to grow seven kind of alternative crop across 21,969 acre ( 8,891 hectare ) of land instead of opium .
global narcotic authority declare myanmar the world 's largest producer of opium in 2001 .
they account for as much as 60 percent of global supply .
