expert state that the rod could produce 3 @-@ 6 atomic bomb in 6 @-@ 8 month .
the iaea state that north korea additionally move 1000 fresh rod into the nuclear reactor as well .
the reactor could produce enough spent rod to construct 1 atomic bomb per year if reactivate .
the experimental nuclear plant in yongbyon be a miniature of electricity @-@ produce nuclear plant in western country but operate on the same principle .
the yongbyon plant produce 5 megawatts .
plant in france produce 1300 megawatts .
the yongbyon plant be 100 km north of the north korean capital pyongyang .
nuclear reactor process --
4 meter fuel rod contain uranium oxide be burn to initiate fission -- the nucleus of the uranium atom be split , release neutron that collide with other atom , create more neutron in a chain reaction .
fission produce immense heat which be apply to water to create steam which drive turbine to generate electricity .
plutonium and other radioactive byproducts of the process accumulate and decrease the effectiveness of the rod until they be spend after 3 @-@ 4 year .
spent rod consisting of highly radioactive plutonium and residual uranium be cool in pool of water for several year to diminish radioactivity and then the plutonium be then recover in nitrate form and convert into oxide .
the recover plutonium can be mix with uranium for reuse in the reactor or use in make nuclear weapon .
nuclear expert state that to make weapon , a high proportion of plutonium 239 ( military grade plutonium , as oppose to the commercial plutonium use in power plant ) must be extract .
