sadagopan state that many sensitive installation such as nuclear and power plant , and missile have an internet protocol address and that once someone hack into the site one can trip the power line or lead plane and missile to their choice destination .
sadagopan add that this type of hack be possible , but there be no need to panic .
sadagopan say it need to be recognize and while we should be sensitive about such threat it should not be sensationalized rather a pragmatic approach should be take .
the u.s. state department say in may 2002 that a computer hacker have infiltrate its e @-@ mail system .
the hacker sent a potentially damage virus to more than 20000 people who receive travel warning electronically .
a 50 @-@ line code of the love bug virus affect more than 2.8 million file monthly .
hackers have send love letter e @-@ mail to all chosen head of state from adolfahitler.com .
pentagon site have denial of service for more than three hour .
india 's premier nuclear research center bhabha atomic resarch center site be disfigure .
sadagopan state that a section of technologist think cyber soldier , cyber policemen and cyber insurance be need .
sadagopan say the threat be overstate and that it be like any other threat , like a foreigner drive on bangalore road .
the threat need to be accept and then education be the next step .
sadagopan say it need to be start today .
it cannot be postpone .
