the attack targeted the popular microsoft database software sql server 2000 .
traffic control site worldwide register decelerate email and other transmission at at 0530 gmt on 20030125 but the private internet @-@ monitor and network protection advise group cert and the national infrastructure protection center state that activity normalize by 1500 gmt .
