security expert state that hackers could have implement the slammer attack on the weekend in order to gauge damage in advance of launch a more devastate attack .
similar attack --
in 20010700 the code red virus affect 300000 computer .
the slammer worm be the largest internet attack since the nimda virus on 20010918 .
slammer be a computer worm .
unlike virus , worm do not require a user to initiate a command such as open an email attachment to infect the computer .
worm carry a self @-@ regenerate mechanism that enable them to multiply rapidly across the web and trigger the flow of copious transmission into computer system .
