the villager be inadvertently involve themselves in drug traffic .
official state that because many farmer be unaware of these law security force make no arrest over poppy cultivation .
prabhakar state --
if the cultivation continue unrestrained kashmir may soon become notorious for narcotic .
this have potential serious consequence as kashmiri youth may become addict to narcotic grown in the region .
poppy cultivation at present be largely organize by group who use their own truck to transport the drug for sale in other part of india .
in 2002 the indian army seize 350 kilogram ( 772 pound ) of narcotic in the kashmir valley .
he will intensify the anti @-@ drug operation .
federal and state official and non @-@ governmental organization should cooperate on the anti @-@ drug campaign and could end the poppy trade in kashmir .
