the time report say that scientist from russia , china , north korea and pakistan plus advance technology have propel iran 's nuclear program much closer to produce a bomb than iraq ever be .
the time point out that some expert predict iran might produce an initial atomic weapon in the next 2 @-@ 3 year .
no one be certain about the actual time frame for iran 's nuclear weapon production .
nuclear material :
the time say a confidential report prepare by the french government in 030500 conclude that iran be surprisingly close to have enrich uranium or plutonium for a bomb .
a foreign intelligence service provide a copy of the report to the time .
the french government warn other government in the report to exercise the most serious vigilance on their export to iran and iranian front company .
the time report say that sample of uranium take by un inspector in iran in 030600 test positive for enrichment level high enough to be consistent with an attempt to build a nuclear weapon .
the iranian government also secretly import 1.8 ton of nuclear material from china in 910000 and process some of this nuclear material in order to manufacture uranium metal .
this uranium would be of no use in iran 's commercial program but would be integral to weapon production .
foreign scientist ' involvement :
the time quote an unnamed middle eastern intelligence official that pakistan 's role be bigger than thought from the begin .
abdul qadeer khan have help iran for year and be a pakistani nuclear scientist regard by the unite state as a purveyor of nuclear secret .
