there be a resort on the caspian coast set aside for the exclusive use of north koreans who be work on nuclear and missile project in iran .
this indicate the number of north koreans work in iran on such project .
russian scientist sometimes travel to iran under false identity and work without the russian government 's approval to help complete a special reactor that could produce weapon @-@ grade plutonium .
new technology :
the report say iranians have also approach european company in recent month to buy device that can manipulate large volume of radioactive material .
this technology be for forge uranium metal and plutonium and switch that could trigger a nuclear weapon .
european intelligence source say list of item the iranians have wish to procure be a strong indication that iran have move to the late stage of weapon development .
