live poultry smuggle undermine who and fao effort to restrict bird flu spread in asia .
fao and who advise country to tighten border security .
smuggler be undermine international effort head by the un world health organization ( who ) and agricultural organization ( fao ) to eradicate bird flu by traffic illegal live poultry that threaten to spread the disease to new area .
attempt to halt bird flu spread --
agriculture and custom official have increase border check throughout the affect region to halt illicit trade .
recent arrest of live poultry smuggler have occur at checkpoint .
most affect asian country have ban the import and export of live and slaughter poultry to prevent the movement of potentially infect chicken and duck across border .
senior fao animal production and health officer in asia hans wagner state --
the fao be concern and well aware that there be copious uncontrolled movement of animal between border in some asian country .
smuggle occur chiefly across the green or uncontrolled border of vietnam , laos , thailand , cambodia , myanmar and china be likely a source for spread the flu and other disease .
authority in vietnam state that smuggle of meat and fruit from china have increase drastically in the past year .
vietnam have experience 9 flu fatality and be the country worst affect by the disease .
prevent smuggle from vietnam be difficult because the country 's extensive land border with china , laos and cambodia be poorly control by a notoriously corrupt custom department .
most nation have tighten border control in accordance with fao and who advisories .
20040120 cambodian authority detain 10 in the southern province of ta keo for import over 150000 duck egg from vietnam .
cambodia have continuously be combating chicken and egg smuggle from vietnam and be on high alert .
20040202 taiwan tighten security against smuggler follow the discovery in 20031200 of h5n1 in duck smuggle from mainland china .
taiwan have previously successfully control an outbreak of the mild h5n2 flu strain .
taiwanese coastguard increase patrol around the island and several island group off the chinese mainland .
approximately 8000 poultry and pig farmer be vaccinate against human flu to prevent it mutate with bird flu strain .
india be free of the disease but have deploy hundred of soldier to the border with myanmar .
myanmar have no report h5n1 case but indian official suspect that poultry could be smuggle through myanmar from thailand .
thailand be one of the country worst affect by the virus .
hong kong authority have increase security along the border with china .
the government state that illegally slaughter poultry import increase by 15 percent from 2002 to 2003 .
the custom and excise department reportedly seize 29266 kilogram of chill or freeze poultry in 2003 compare with 1749 kilogram in 2002 .
custom spokesman richard law state that the department perform frequent check on smuggle activity and have now increase effort to inspect cargo .
the h5n1 flu strain have cause 13 death and report outbreak in 10 country .
