shalgam state that libyan official have have the material to produce weapon of mass destruction but have decide to abandon tripoli 's weapon of mass destruction program .
foreign minister abdel rahman shalgam state on 10 february 2004 during a visit to london that libyan official have all the mean to make weapon of mass destruction but never decide to produce the weapon .
shalgam 's visit to london be the first by a libyan foreign minister since 1969 .
