shalgam state the program 's abandonment be not impose on libyan official .
shalgam state libyan official want american and british aid which would be more beneficial to libya than make weapon of mass destruction .
straw state the libyan official ' decision be a courageous step and that the announcement of the decision pave the way for the former pariah state of libya 's reintegration into the international community .
straw state that the announcement show that problem of proliferation can with good will be tackle through discussion and engagement .
straw state the libyan official ' decision should benefit the whole region and make the world a safe place .
