a draft report prepare for the eu executive state that the european union should massively increase research on security issue in order to better protect civilian from terrorist attack .
the report be create by a work group include research commissioner philippe busquin and enterprise commissioner erkki liikanen .
it recommend that up to two billion euros be spend per year on a vast pan @-@ european research program .
the european security research program ( esrp ) would receive eu fund begin in 2007 .
it be the most ambitious of several recommendation the group be likely to issue when it present its final conclusion in two or three week .
the draft report recommend start security research fund with one billion euros per year in 2007 .
it will then slowly increase the annual budget to two billion euros .
european spend currently lag behind the unite state .
the unite state ' homeland security department receive one billion dollar annually plus research credit from the defense department .
the report state that there be no reason why european security research should not be fund at a level similar to the unite state .
the european commission strategy allow for a preliminary period of study and pilot project from 2004 to 2006 .
it promote eu @-@ wide synergies in research on top safety issue include protection against bio @-@ terrorism and improve networking between civilian and military authority across the continent .
65 million euros have be earmark for the 2004 @-@ 2006 phase of the research program accord to an exploratory plan of action present by the commission on february 3 , 2004 .
