international ; government ; crime
desire admission into the european union , albanian government increase effort against drug traffic by strengthen law , seize illegal drug , and investigate possibly corrupt police official .
under the pressure of the european union the albanian government have escalate its fight against drug traffic by prepare a new strategy to halt the smuggle of hashish and heroin over albanian territory from asia towards the west .
a recent eu report on albania state the situation in albania , which have remain an important country for the traffic of narcotic , be worrisome .
the report suggest the tirana government adopt an efficient strategy in the government 's effort against drug traffic .
albanian interior minister igli toska state --
the fight against drug traffic will be the albanian government 's main challenge in 2004 .
the albanian government have be work on a project of national strategy which will require international support and cooperation .
albania 's geographic position , albania 's trade with turkey and greece , and the situation after the kosovo war be all element albanian criminal group profit from , thereby make albania an important stop for the transit of narcotic .
in july 2004 the albanian government plan to present a set of anti @-@ mafia law which will allow confiscation of property belong to person involve in criminal and illegal activity .
albanian justice minister adrian dvorani state the anti @-@ mafia law also provide for the special protection of witness or people involve in illegal traffic who decide to testify and will enable a more efficient strategy .
albanian official aspire to eu membership .
the albanian government have make a significant development in the government 's fight against drug smuggler in 2004 .
in 2003 albanian police infiltrate an international drug network operate between kosovo , macedonia , albania and italy and control by the kosovo albanian and turkish criminal group link with the calabrian mafia organization n'drangheta .
in may 2004 approximately 100 policemen -- 25 of them in top position -- be dismiss on suspect tie with organized crime .
60 others have be investigate on similar charge .
toska state there will be no smuggler without corrupt policemen and toska announce tough measure against policemen and security official link with criminal group .
the eu report quote the name of several albanian politician directly or indirectly involve in drug traffic but no measure have so far be take against the politician .
albanian police force have seize more than 200 kilo ( 440 pound ) of heroin and around 8 ton of cannabis between november 2003 and may 2004 , double that which be seize in 2003 .
expert say the figure of drug seize be insignificant compare to the estimate quantity of narcotic that be smuggle through albania .
international police expert based in tirana estimate the value of the narcotic in transit at over 2 billion dollar ( about 1.6 billion euros ) per year .
expert estimate the amount smuggle through albania make up approximately 25 to 30 percent of the narcotic smuggle into the european market from the balkans .
albanian police official xhavit shala state albanian smuggler be link to the international criminal organization like ( the italian ) sacra corona unita , cosa nostra , the turkish , russian , macedonian and kosovar mafia , and the colombian drug cartel .
bujar mema of the albanian interpol office state that drug smuggler have reappear due to increase consumption of narcotic in europe and the production of opium from afghanistan , which have reach the level of the year before the us intervention in 2001 with 3600 ton produce in 2003 .
