critic of estonia 's response may not be aware that traffic on some estonian site be increase by 1 million .
impose temporary restriction on internet traffic from abroad be inevitable .
mcglade 's comment on the estonian response be make in geneva ahead of a unite nation conference on global access to information technology .
mcglade state that attack on state and private websites should be handle in a systematic way instead of by restrict access .
mcglade state that there be technology that the eu agency deploy in an effort to avoid restrict access to government websites .
the eu agency will be in contact with the estonian government to advise on possible defense measure .
estonia be a world pioneer in it solution .
estonia rank higher than the 15 older eu member and just behind the unite state on a world bank list of country that be advance in prepare for a knowledge @-@ based society .
aarelaid state --
access to critical websites be never restrict .
estonia be prepare to keep critical websites accessible in any situation but that during a massive cyber attack some websites like that of the estonian agriculture ministry be of a lower priority to keep accessible to visitor from abroad .
