a senior government official of spain state that the spanish government will use informal discussion outside of meeting at the osce conference to seek a compromise to russia 's threat to suspend its participation in the conventional force in europe treaty .
the conventional force in europe treaty be consider a key arm control treaty .
the treaty limit the deployment of tank , aircraft and other heavy weapon across the continent .
approximately 40 foreign minister from the 56 @-@ nation security and democracy agency osce be participate in the 2 @-@ day meet that commence 28 november 2007 in madrid , spain .
spain currently hold the rotate presidency of the osce .
earlier in 2007 the government of russia state that as of 12 december 2007 it would cease implementation of the conventional force in europe treaty .
russian president vladimir putin state that the decision be a response to u.s. plan to establish missile defense site in eastern europe and to nato 's failure to ratify an amend version of the treaty .
spain 's director for foreign affair for europe and north america jose pons state that a meet of high @-@ rank official from nation that have sign the treaty would take place on 27 november 2007 in an effort to reach a solution .
pons state to reporter --
the meet must be handle with prudence because the issue be difficult .
there have be many contact between the most concern country with the unite state and russia .
there have be advance but no solution .
last week spanish foreign minister miguel angel moratinos state that there be a desire among all party include russia to reach an agreement on the issue .
the conventional force in europe treaty be sign on november 19 , 1990 in paris by the north atlantic treaty organization ( nato ) and the warsaw pact .
nato and warsaw pact nation be the 2 oppose bloc during the cold war .
the treaty be amend in 1999 after the collapse of the soviet union .
russia ratify the update treaty in 2004 but the unite state and other nato member have refuse to do so argue that moscow must first fulfill obligation to withdraw force from georgia and from moldova 's separatist region of trans @-@ dniester .
