russian federation ( ru ) ; kazakhstan ( kz )
politics ; international ; weapon
russia 's decision to suspend its participation in the conventional force in europe treaty and kazakhstan 's bid to assume the chairmanship of the organization for security and cooperation in europe will be the focus of the upcoming annual osce conference .
spain as current president will lead meeting to reach solution .
russia 's decision to suspend its participation in a key arm control treaty and kazakhstan 's bid for chairmanship of the organization for security and cooperation in europe ( osce ) will be 2 of the major issue discuss at the osce conference in madrid , spain to occur on 29 november 2007 and 30 november 2007 .
the osce conference will be attend by foreign minister of the 56 member nation .
the osce monitor issue regard international security and democracy .
earlier in 2007 the government of russia announce it will suspend implementation of the conventional force in europe treaty as of 12 december 2007 .
the treaty be a key pact limit the deployment of tank , aircraft and other weapon across europe .
russian president vladimir putin have state the suspension be a response to u.s. plan to establish missile defense site in poland and the czech republic and to the deployment of u.s. and other nato force in former soviet republic in europe .
the osce feature a rotate presidency and spain be the current president .
spain plan to hold a meet outside the conference agenda in order to reach a solution regard russia 's plan suspension of the treaty .
russia and the u.s. be member of the osce .
last week spanish foreign minister miguel angel moratinos state that there be a desire among all party include russia to reach an agreement .
the 1990 treaty originally set limit on weapon for nato and warsaw pact country .
the treaty be revise in 1999 after the collapse of the soviet union .
to be discuss will be the role of the osce 's election monitor unit follow its decision earlier in november 2007 to boycott the parliamentary election in russia to be hold on 02 december 2007 .
the osce 's office for democratic institution and human right ( odihr ) defend the decision to boycott cite russian authority ' delay in issue visa and unwarranted restriction impose on the osce observation mission .
on 26 november 2007 putin state that the osce have canceled its plan vote monitor on the recommendation of the u.s. state department and that the aim be to discredit the election .
russia have deny obstruct the observer and have state the election will conform with russian law .
kazakhstan 's bid to assume the rotate chairmanship of the osce in 2009 be expect to be a major topic of discussion at the conference .
kazakhstan 's bid for the osce chairmanship be the first bid from a former soviet union nation .
the government of kazakhstan have lobby for the chairmanship argue it have a stable political situation , multilateral foreign policy and strong economy distinguish it from other former soviet country .
several osce member state have question kazakhstan 's democratic credentials .
kazakhstan be an oil @-@ rich country .
head of the assessment risk group in kazakhstan 's capital almaty be dosym satpayev .
satpayev state that kazakhstan 's chance of win its bid for the chairmanship be considerably reduce after its last general election be not recognize as conform to osce standard .
kazakhstan president nursultan nazarbayev 's political party nur otan win all the seat in the parliamentary election held in august 2007 .
the choice of the osce chairmanship be make by consensus .
opposition by 1 country would be enough to deny kazakhstan the chairmanship .
british newspaper the financial time report on 27 november 2007 that osce official will offer kazakhstan a deal organize by spain under which the country would assume the rotate chairmanship in 2010 or 2011 .
osce spokeswoman virginie coulloudon state that such a deal be 1 scenario among 5 or 6 others .
kazakhstan 's foreign ministry insist the country be still seek the chairmanship for 2009 .
