15 people be sentence to death in vietnam for drug traffic in two different trial on november 29 , 2007 .
court official state on november 30 , 2007 that 15 people have be sentence to death in vietnam for drug traffic in two different trial .
11 people include 4 women be give the death penalty in hanoi for traffic 440 kilogram or 968 pound of heroin .
7 other member of the same drug traffic ring be jail for life and 4 receive term from 17 month to 20 year at the 11 day trial which end on november 29 , 2007 .
the ring be find guilty of sell heroin in hanoi and ho chi minh city from 2000 until the arrest early in 2007 .
on november 29 , 2007 in the central province of nghe an a court sentence 4 people to death and jail 3 others for life after the individual be find guilty of traffic heroin accord to an official at the provincial court after a 2 day trial .
vietnam give the death penalty to anyone caught with more than 600 gram of heroin or more than 20 kilogram of opium .
78 people have be put on death row in vietnam since the begin of 2007 .
in 2006 vietnam sentence at least 71 people to death mostly for drug traffic and murder .
vietnam be a communist nation .
