narcotic ; crime
iran official hang 2 convict drug trafficker and 1 convict rapist in public in qom on 2 december 2007 .
a large number of recent execution in iran have be in public .
state news agency irna report that iranian official publicly hang 2 convict drug trafficker and 1 convict rapist in the clerical city of qom on 2 december 2007 .
the drug trafficker be identify as yahya madadi and atollah poolzehi and be hang for traffic more than 100 kilogram ( 220 pound ) of heroin .
the rapist be identify as hossein safarlou and have also be convict of drug traffic .
police force commander of qom province rahim khorshid state to the crowd during the hanging that the police be serious in the policy of decisively combating thug and drug trafficker .
accord to an afp count compile from press report the hanging bring the total number of execution in iran in 2007 to 273 .
execution have increase in iran in 2007 as official enforce a campaign against what the authority call thug such as drug @-@ trafficker , extortionist and rapist .
