france ( fr ) ; algeria ( dz )
international ; government ; energy ; politics ; money ; business
french president tour algeria to sign billion of dollar in oil and gas deal and a nuclear accord .
sarkozy call colonialist occupation unjust but refrain from apologize for atrocity .
on 04 december 2007 on day 2 of a state visit to algeria by french president nicolas sarkozy the government of france and algeria sign billion of dollar of oil and gas deal and a nuclear accord .
one of the purpose of the visit be an effort to address damage done to algeria by french colonialist conquest and occupation .
on the tour sarkozy promote a new economic partnership with the energy @-@ rich north african nation and underscore historic tension between france and its former colony algeria .
on 03 december 2007 sarkozy be applaud at an algiers business forum for a speech denounce colonialism as unjust .
sarkozy do not apologize for the atrocity commit by french troop and settler during algeria 's 1954 @-@ 1962 war of independence .
follow a visit to the world heritage archaeological site of tipaza west of algiers sarkozy 's delegation hold meeting in which contract worth approximately 5 billion u.s. dollar be finalize .
algerian and french official sign a wide @-@ range accord on civil nuclear energy that address the use and development of nuclear energy for peaceful end .
the civil nuclear energy accord be describe by a french source as the first between the government of france and an arab @-@ muslim country .
the deal address research , technology transfer and electricity production , as well as prospect and dig for uranium .
among the myriad gas and oil accord french oil company total sign a deal to invest 1.5 billion u.s. dollar ( 1 billion euro ) in a new petrochemical plant in algeria .
accord to the deal total in partnership with algeria 's sonatrach will develop a plant at the port of arzan west of the algiers at a total estimate cost of 3 billion u.s. dollar .
gaz de france ( gdf ) state that it extend its exist gas contract with sonatrach from 2013 to 2019 in a deal worth approximately 2.5 billion euro per year at current market price .
as head of a consortium that include the egyptian firm orascom the company alstom finalize a deal with algeria for a combined cycle gas turbine power plant to be build in the western terga region .
france rule algeria from 1830 to 1962 .
algeria become 1 of france 's proudest possession .
france populate algeria with 10 s of 1000 s of settler .
algeria be the second biggest country in africa .
the government of france and its former colony have maintain an uneasy relationship since 1962 .
45 year later plan for a friendship treaty remain stall over france 's refusal to apologize for past event .
in his speech on 03 december 200 sarkozy state that the colonial system be profoundly unjust and contrary to the 3 found word of the french republic which be freedom , equality and brotherhood .
sarkozy state that within that system there be many men and women who love algeria before they be force to leave it .
algerian interior minister yazid zerhouni state that while sarkozy 's remark be a sign of progress they be not sufficient .
during a state lunch with sarkozy the algerian president abdelaziz bouteflika be more positive .
bouteflika call sarkozy mr. president and dear friend .
bouteflika state that this visit would allow algeria and france to overcome problem in the relationship .
bouteflika stress the potential for scientific , technological and economic cooperation between france and algeria state that both country have a duty to promote an exchange of people , idea and wealth .
bouteflika state that the estimate 3 million algerian migrant and their french @-@ born descendant should serve as a bridge between the 2 country .
