new light of myanmar newspaper state --
police and soldier raid 3 poppy field in eastern shan state which be part of the golden triangle region on the border of myanmar , laos and thailand .
the golden triangle region be 1 of the world 's biggest producer of opium .
the authority have already destroy approximately 70 of the 140 acre ( 57 hectare ) plant with poppy and plan be under way to destroy the remain poppy field .
myanmar be the 2 nd largest opium producer in the world after afghanistan .
the un office on drug and crime ( unodc ) state that in 2006 opium production jump by 46 percent after year of sharp decline .
myanmar government have state myanmar will become opium @-@ free by 2014 .
the unodc state myanmar 's production have fall behind afghanistan in recent year and now account for only 6 percent of the world opium market , compare to 63 percent in 1998 .
the unodc state thailand have be opium free for 20 year while laos have slash opium production by 94 percent since 1997 .
