vietnam ( vn )
international ; narcotic ; crime ; government
vietnam have sentence 43 drug smuggler to receive the death penalty from 071128 until 071228 .
a vietnam court official state on 071228 that vietnam have sentence 8 heroin trafficker and have raise total number drug smuggler to receive the death penalty to 43 people from 071128 until 071228 .
a hanoi people 's court clerk state to the agence france @-@ presse that the hanoi people 's court jail 29 other people in the most recent mass trial for traffic heroin across vietnam 's mountainous northern region for over two year .
a hanoi people 's court clerk state to the agence france @-@ presse that 18 of the 29 people jail in the most recent mass trial receive life sentence .
during the most recent mass trial in hanoi people 's court it be state that the drug smuggle gang work on a common drug traffic route to smuggle the heroin from the northwestern son la province near the lao border to the capital hanoi , the port of haiphong and to ho chi minh city .
since late 071100 the vietnamese court have sentence at least 43 people to death and jail score more in several group trial against heroin smuggle syndicate , extend family and clan network .
vietnam 's police state that the vietnamese police have uncover more than 8200 drug traffic case involve 12500 offender in 070000 .
the vietnam news agency report that the ministry of public security state that foreigner involve in drug traffic case in vietnam come mostly from laos , cambodia , australia , china , the unite state and taiwan .
the vietnam news agency report that the ministry of public security state that police admit that drug traffic into vietnam be increase but action to prevent and stop the drug traffic along the border remain limit .
vietnam 's mountainous northwest region account for almost half of the confiscate heroin in vietnam while the chinese border area be identify as another highly active drug smuggle region in vietnam .
expert state that heroin be the most popular illegal drug in vietnam and heroin be the lead cause of hiv infection because heroin be often inject with share needle .
expert state that most heroin in vietnam come from the golden triangle of country that include myanmar and laos .
communist vietnam and most asian country impose harsh penalty for drug smuggler .
people catch with over 600 grammes of heroin or 20 kilogrammes of opium in vietnam be sentence to death by fire squad .
opium be the raw material use to make heroin .
vietnam have a century @-@ old history of opium use and the cultivation of opium be vastly expand under french colonial rule . during the vietnam war the heroin that travel from the nearby golden triangle to western market rise sharply .
the post @-@ vietnam war vietnamese government mostly eradicate large @-@ scale opium cultivation and in 040000 estimate that little more than 30 hectare of opium poppy field remain in vietnam .
the opium poppy field remain in 040000 in vietnam be mostly grow by remote and poor ethnic minority villager .
expert state that vietnam 's proximity to myanmar and laos and vietnam 's porous border and long coastline have make vietnam a major drug transit country .
myanmar and laos be still the second and third largest opium producer after afghanistan .
domestic drug abuse in vietnam have rise sharply since the decade of 900000 .
the unite nation 's office for drug and crime control state that domestic drug abuse in vietnam have rise sharply especially in the city where heroin continue to be the prefer drug among younger drug abusers .
in a 050000 report the unite nation 's office for drug and crime control state that opium smoke have long give way to heroin smoke and increasingly heroin injection in vietnam .
heroin injection currently cause approximately 60 percent of know hiv infection in vietnam .
the state @-@ run english language vietnam news daily report on 071228 that in the vietnamese @-@ lao border province of dien bien the authority have recently launch a major campaign against the rise in heroin smuggle activity .
villager in dien bien province have be ask to sign pledge not to grow opium poppy , not to use opium , and not to help smuggler carry or sell drug .
the state @-@ run english language vietnam news daily report that drug trafficker have become more sophisticated and dangerous and that some drug trafficker be ready to attack police with firearm and grenade .
