china ( cn ) ; democratic people 's republic of korea ( kp )
proliferation ; international ; military
us expert report chinese plan to dispatch troop to north korea and secure north korea 's nuclear arsenal in the event of instability .
a report compile by expert from the center for strategic and international study , the us institute of peace and the asia foundation state that china have contingency plan to dispatch chinese people 's liberation army ( pla ) troop to north korea and secure nuclear weapon in the event of instability in north korea .
the expert visit china 20070600 to confer with chinese military researcher .
the report state --
china 's strong preference be to receive formal authorization and coordinate closely with the un in any possible intervention .
china would take unilateral action to restore stability if the international community do not react in a timely manner as the internal order in north korea deteriorate rapidly .
the report state --
pla researcher claim that contingency plan exist for the pla to perform three possible mission in north korea -- humanitarian , peacekeeping and environmental control .
the environmental control measure be intend to clean up nuclear contamination result from a strike on north korean nuclear facility near the sino @-@ north korean border and to secure nuclear weapon and fissile material .
the report state --
china 's main priority in the event of instability in north korea would be prevention of an influx of refugee by assure supply of food and strengthen border control .
pla officer state that they would attempt to close the border but admit a lack of confidence that they could do so successfully because the border extend 866 mile and can be easily penetrate .
north korea reportedly possess up to 10 nuclear bomb but be currently involve in a denuclearization program in return for energy aid and diplomatic and security guarantee under a six @-@ party mechanism involve the unite state , china , russia , south korea and japan .
the program recently encounter difficulty when the us accuse north korea of fail to meet the 20071231 deadline for a full declaration of nuclear programs .
the report be publish on the websites of us think tank the center for strategic and international study and the us institute of peace and be entitle " keep an eye on an unruly neighbor -- chinese view of economic reform and stability in north korea ."
