hamas @-@ izz al @-@ din al @-@ qassem and palestinian islamic jihad be fight to end the israeli occupation of palestine .
lashkar @-@ e @-@ tayyiba be engage in a guerrilla war with indian security force to create an independent islamic state in the dispute territory of kashmir .
the statement say japan have restrict the transaction of a total of 12 organization and individual suspect of terrorist activity .
another 293 be believe to have tie to afghanistan 's taliban militia .
the taliban be accuse of shelter osama bin laden .
the unite state have name bin laden as the mastermind of the september 11 terrorist attack on washington and new york .
the japanese government announce in october 2001 that japan have freeze three taliban bank account in japan hold about dlrs 600,000 .
another 28 account amounting to about 18 million yen ( about dlrs 136,000 ) be freeze because they be suspect of be connect to the taliban .
