russian federation ( ru )
international ; space ; military
ret. lt. @-@ gen. anatoly sokolov announce -- soviet @-@ built a @-@ 135 missile defense system around moscow be obsolete and inefficient .
he say russia be not strong enough to modernize the exist antimissile system and should build new missile defense technology instead .
15 april 2002 retire russian space force general ret. lt. @-@ gen. anatoly sokolov announce --
soviet @-@ built a @-@ 135 missile defense system around moscow be obsolete and inefficient .
the a @-@ 135 system be the only such system in the world .
the a @-@ 135 system should be remove .
the a @-@ 135 system be unable to provide protection of the area or the country .
ussr deploy a @-@ 35 anti @-@ ballistic missile system in 1974 .
the a @-@ 35 --
be deploy around moscow .
consisted of radars and 64 missile interceptor .
be continually modify with independently @-@ targeted multiple warhead .
a @-@ 135 launch in 1994 as latest version of a @-@ 35 .
a @-@ 135 include long @- and medium @-@ range missile interceptor .
the anti @-@ ballistic missile ( abm ) treaty allow the us and russia to protect a single site with no more than 100 interceptor .
russia 's missile defense system comply with the abm treaty .
in 1970 s the us have a similar system to protect missile field in north dakota .
the us have destroy this system .
the abm treaty bar a nationwide missile shield of the kind the us want to deploy .
in december 2001 president george w. bush warn russia that the us would withdraw from the abm treaty in 6 month .
russian president vladimir putin state --
us withdrawal from the abm treaty be not a threat to russian security .
us withdrawal from the abm would hurt global stability .
russian official have say recently that the moscow missile defense system could be upgrade in the next few year ,
sokolov state --
russian government should not modernize the old missile defense system but build new missile defense technology instead .
modernization would be costly .
russia be not strong enough to modernize the exist antimissile system .
russia have lose several soviet @-@ built long @-@ range radars essential for effective operation of an anti @-@ missile system .
a new anti @-@ missile system in belarus would be inadequate .
sokolov previously serve as a top commander with russia 's space force .
