head of the european space agency 's technology transfer program pierre brisson state that the european space agency will have to ask the european commission before confirm ukraine can join the program .
pierre brisson also state that the european commission will much likely issue approval by august 5 , 2002 and work on the project could start on december 5 , 2002 .
the ukrainian government must also approve the ukraine 's participation in the program but deputy director of ukraine 's national space agency eduard kuznetsov state that no problem be expect because of president leonid kuchma 's pro @-@ european goal .
the european space agency 's endorsement follow ukraine 's formal announcement to bid to join nato on may 29 , 2002 .
pierre brisson lead a team of european expert on a visit to kiev to discuss commercial application of ukrainian space technology with representative of the national space agency of ukraine , scientist and business leader .
