embraer open a new factory in the sao paulo state of brazil in order to better compete to win a contract with the brazilian air force .
embraer inaugurate a new factory to build corporate jet and expand into the military aviation sector on june 11 , 2002 .
mauricio betelho state that the factory will allow embraer to enter business sector it have not yet enter .
the factory be locate in an area call gaviao peixoto in the sao paulo state in brazil .
gaviao peixoto be a small orange and sugar cane farm town of 4500 inhabitant about 300 kilometers or 180 mile northwest of sao paulo .
this location be call ideal to test military aircraft at supersonic speed .
embraer be invest 150 million dollar over 10 year to upgrade the factory 's technology so that the factory can produce embraer 's new legacy corporate jet and a range of military aircraft .
the military aircraft include the emb @-@ 145 reconnaissance and alx super tucano train plane .
the factory contain a 5 kilometer or 3 mile long test runway which be the longest in the southern hemisphere .
embraer president mauricio betelho state that the factory be expect to employ 1000 people by 2003 and 3000 people over the next decade .
the factory be expect to attract investment by the jetmaker 's supplier .
kawaski heavy industry of japan be the first supplier to invest in the factory .
this supplier will use the factory to make wing for embraer 's new 08 seat erj 190 @/@ 195 passenger jet .
mauricio betelho state kawaski heavy industry be likely to be just the first of several supplier to invest in the plant .
embraer be the world 's 4 th largest aircraft manufacturer and brazil 's top exporter .
