win the contract would also allow embraer to export assemble mirage .
the competitor include lockheed martin ' f @-@ 16 c , the jas @-@ 39 gripen built by a u.k . @-@ swedish consortium and two russian plane call the mig @-@ 29 and the sukhoi su @-@ 35 .
air force expert be say to prefer the sukhoi fighter but botelho state that national sovereignty should play an important role in the result .
sao paulo state be brazil 's richest and most industralized state .
