musharraf pledge to stop cross @-@ border infiltration because of pressure from the unite state .
the unite state fear the kashmir crisis could trigger a full @-@ scale conflict between india and pakistan .
the dispute over kashmir begin when india and pakistan gain independence from britain in 1947 .
the two country both have nuclear weapon and have fight two war over kashmir .
there be increase tension of war between india and pakistan after an attack on an indian army camp .
the attack kill 34 people and be one of the deadliest single assault since 1989 .
in 1989 militant launch an insurgency in indian @-@ control kashmir seek independence or a merger with islamic pakistan .
