unite state ( us ) ; south africa ( za ) ; syrian arab republic ( sy ) ; korea , democratic people 's republic of ( kp ) ; libyan arab jamahiriya ( ly ) ; iran ( ir ) ; pakistan ( pk )
weapon ; terrorism ; international ; politics ; proliferation
the unite nation security council unanimously approve a resolution urge increase effort to keep weapon of mass destruction out of the hand of terrorist and black marketeer .
on 080425 the unite nation security council unanimously approve a resolution urge increase effort to keep weapon of mass destruction out of the hand of terrorist and black marketeer .
the security council resolution call on all state to fully implement a security council resolution adopt in 040400 require all 192 unite nation member state to adopt law to prevent non @-@ state actor from acquire nuclear , chemical or biological weapon .
the security council resolution note that some unnamed country have not file a report on the member nation effort to adopt these law .
the report be due to the unite nation in 041000 .
the 080425 security council resolution stress the need to enhance the coordination of national , regional and international effort to strengthen a global response to the serious challenge of keep weapon from terrorist and the threat to international security .
the 040400 security council resolution be adopt to close a loophole in global effort to prevent the proliferation of weapon of mass destruction .
international treaty targeted weapon proliferation by government until resolution 1540 be adopt in 040000 there be no legal instrument to prevent terrorist , criminal scientist , black marketeer and other non @-@ state actor from obtain weapon of mass destruction .
resolution 1540 be introduce as the international atomic energy agency be investigate a vast black market in nuclear equipment and technology .
the black market investigation be encourage by pakistan 's admission in 040200 that pakistan 's lead nuclear scientist have pass technology to iran , libya and north korea .
pakistan 's lead nuclear scientist , be abdul qadeer khan .
resolution 1540 require all country to adopt law to prevent non @-@ state actor from manufacture , acquire or traffic in nuclear , biological or chemical weapon , the material to make them , and the missile and other system to deliver them .
resolution 1540 require all country to take measure to account for and secure these weapon , missile and other weapon material .
resolution 1540 also demand that country develop border control and step up law enforcement effort to detect , deter , prevent and combat the illicit traffic and brokering of weapon of mass destruction .
all country be require to submit a report within 6 month to a security council committee monitor implementation of esolution 1540 .
the resolution adopt on 080425 extend the resolution 1540 committee 's mandate until 110425 and again call upon all state that have not yet present a first report on step the state have take or intend to take to implement resolution 1540 to submit such a report to the 1540 committee without delay .
the 080425 resolution emphasize the importance for all state to fully implement resolution 1540 .
the 080425 resolution also call on the resolution 1540 committee to continue to intensify its effort to promote the full implementation by all state by reach out to country , facilitate technical assistance , and promote share experience and lesson learn .
the security council state that not all state have present to the resolution 1540 committee the state 's national report on implementation of resolution 1540 and that the full implementation of resolution 1540 by all state be a long @-@ term task that will require continuous effort at national , regional and international level .
the security council state that full implementation of resolution 1540 by all state include the adoption of national law and measure to ensure implementation of the resolution 1540 inspire national law .
dumisani kumalo state that many develop country find the report requirement for resolution 1540 and other resolution onerous when they be try to provide food , health care and job for the people of develop country .
dumisani kumalo be the current security council president and south africa 's unite nation ambassador .
dumisani kumalo state that one of the thing that south africa be happy about be that country must cooperate in deal with the network that may be spread illict nuclear and other weapon .
the 080425 resolution be approve on the day that mohamed elbaradei angrily criticize israel for bomb an alleged syrian nuclear facility , chastise the unite state for withhold information on the alleged syrian nuclear facility , and state that the international atomic energy agency would investigate the allegation of the syrian nuclear facility .
mohamed elbaradei be the international atomic energy agency chief .
