7 nato ally to sign agreement to create a cyber defense research center in estonia .
expert from nato member state will be recruit to conduct research and train on cyber warfare and will be prepare to assist ally with response to the grow threat of cyber attack .
7 nato ally be prepare to sign a deal on 14 may 2008 to create a research center in tallinn , estonia to improve the nato alliance 's defenses against cyber attack .
cyber attack be consider a grow threat to military and civilian computer network .
in 2007 estonia experience an unprecedented number of cyber attack that disable government and corporate computer network .
the attack occur after a dispute between the government of russia and estonia over the relocation of a soviet war memorial .
many estonians suspect the russian government be responsible for the cyber attack but the government of russia deny involvement .
defense chief from estonia , latvia , lithuania , germany , italy , spain and slovakia will sign the agreement to provide staff and fund for the center .
the unite state will join the project as an observer and other nato nation may join later .
sign of the agreement be a peripheral issue of the meet of chief of defense staff from the 26 ally country of nato .
the meet be expect to focus on nato mission in afghanistan and kosovo .
the general will also discuss cooperation with balkan and former soviet nation include russia and ukraine .
the cyber defense center will be operational in august 2008 with the formal open plan for 2009 .
a staff of 30 specialist will conduct research and train on cyber warfare and will be prepare to assist nato member with response to any future cyber attack .
head of the center major raul rikk state to the associate press in tallinn --
the attack against estonia last year be cyber terrorism .
the mission of the center be to create new capability to fight new threat .
expert will be recruit from various nato member state and from various sector include information technology , science , military and finance .
estonia be 1 of europe 's most internet @-@ savvy nation .
estonia propose creation of the center in 2003 but it be not until after the cyber attack of 2007 that nato leader be convince it be need .
