fluhr say in a statement : " stubhub 's business model be an excellent fit with ebay , and we have admire ebay for a long time . "
over the past two year , as investor be concern about the slowdown in ebay 's online auction business , its poor management , slow business expansion , and other factor , its market value have be dwindle .
in succession ebay acquire internet phone service skype and online price - comparison company shopping.com .
stubhub mainly operate ticket brokerage to major event .
in 2006 its ticket sale be 400 million us dollar with annual profit reach 100 million us dollar .
ticket seller sell ticket on this website must pay a 15 percent fee , while buyer also have to pay a 10 percent commission to stubhub .
