this shift be drive by the combination of ( a ) escalate world consumption of petroleum , especially in rapidly develop economy like china and india , and ( b ) the peak of global oil production capacity , the increase expense of exploit the remote and isolate oil reserve that remain , and terrorist / political instability in oil - produce country .
this be not the oil company ' fault .
this be not dick cheney 's fault .
