the project management system of the three gorge project will introduce scientific management method and advanced computer technology of the mai corp. of canada , which use the project database management system as the core component in its control and management of the whole process of design , plan , contract , finance , goods and material , equipment , construction and installation of each subproject of the three gorge project .
in october of 1995 , youmei lu , the general manager of the three gorge project development corporation of china , go to canada to sign the related business contract .
this export credit project be entrust to the bank of china as the acting bank , and its commercial agent be the china electronics import and export corporation .
on february 28 th , the three gorge branch of the bank of china sign the agreement contract with the yangtze river three gorge project development corporation of china to transfer the loan of the project .
