on the occasion of the 30 th anniversary of the establishment of asean , the head of the nine asean country and the head of china , japan and south korea hold an informal meet in kuala lumpur , capital of malaysia , on the 15 th .
the next day , the head of china , japan and south korea hold informal meeting again with the head of the asean country separately .
this informal meet of head of eastern asian country , the first time in history , be a good start .
after the end of the cold war , asean confront new international and regional situation and comprehensively adjust its development strategy and foreign relation strategy , and increasingly become a cooperative organization in the southeast asia region based on economic cooperation and integrate politics , economy and security .
asean , with china , japan and south korea , strengthen their cooperation and jointly plan development , become a force that hold the balance .
therefore , the hold of the informal meet of head of the country in eastern asia possess important significance in promote cooperation between all country , in safeguard regional and global security , and in accelerate the development towards world multi @-@ polarization .
the development of country can not be separate from the region , and that of the region can not be separate from the globe .
discard old concept and establish new international political and economic order conform with the main trend of the time in which people of all country demand peace , request development , seek stability and promote cooperation .
to correctly understand the relationship between economic development , political stability , social harmony and national security , to diligently promote all country , region and the whole world to travel on the road of peaceful development , to jointly discuss east asian economic cooperation in the 21 st century and forecast the future development of eastern asia be subject be discuss at this informal meet of head of state in eastern asia .
peace be a precondition to economic development .
without a peaceful environment , any construction undertake would be impossible to discuss .
only when long - term peace be realize can the realization of sustain development be possible .
therefore it be necessary to breed a new kind of security concept and to seek new method to safeguard peace .
to establish relation between country on the basis of the five principle , namely mutual respect of sovereignty and integrity of territory , non @-@ aggression , non @-@ interference in internal affair , equality and mutual benefit , and peaceful coexistence , be the political basis and precondition for global and regional security .
that all country strengthen their mutual benefit and cooperation in the field of economy , open up to each other , eliminate inequality and discriminatory policy in economic and trade transaction , gradually narrow the development gap between country and strive for joint prosperity be the economic basis for global and regional security .
that all country promote mutual understand and trust through dialogue and cooperation , and promise to settle dispute and conflict between country in peaceful way be a realistic way to ensure peace and security .
this year some country in eastern asia encounter financial turmoil and have have some difficulty in their economic development , but the economic basis of east asian country be still good and advantageous factor for economic development still exist .
in the course of this meet , leader of east asian country unanimously support the suggestion to expand local trade and investment .
it be believe that after review experience and implement proper adjustment , the economy of eastern asia will definitely continue to move forward in development .
the east asian country be not entirely without conflict and dispute .
but in order to safeguard fundamental benefit to the people of all east asian country , and to promote the lofty cause of peace and development for mankind , we must progressively strengthen the east asian cooperation .
chairman zemin jiang solemnly elaborate on china 's stand at this meet .
he emphatically point out that " we should uphold the principle of mutual respect , equal participation , mutual benefit , and co @-@ development ; we should strengthen cooperation in economy and technology , especially in the field of new high level technology , and establish reasonable regional economic structure , and form a mode of economic cooperation on the basis of learn from others ' strength and offset others ' weakness , and mutual benefit from advantage , balance interest , and practicing non @-@ exclusiveness and non @-@ discrimination ; and we should strengthen trust , broaden common understand , seek common point while maintain difference , and resolve dispute appropriately through friendly dialogue and consultation to guarantee the region 's peace and stability . "
everything be difficult at the very begin .
with this good start , people have good reason to believe that the coordination and cooperation between east asian country will certainly show more hopeful prospect in the near future .
( end )
