xinhua news agency , washington , dc , december 21 , by wire ( reporter jingsheng zhai )
on the 21 st , the international monetary fund release here a provisional assessment report , and once again lower its forecast for the speed of growth of the world economy for this year and next year .
the report hold that the effect that the asian bank crisis be have on the world economy be even more serious than previously estimate .
it estimate that for the world economy this year 's rate of growth would be 4.1 % , next year fall to 3.5 % , and that this year be the year with the slowest growth in the last 5 year .
compare to the forecast that the above - mention organization publish in october , this be lower by 0.1 and 0.8 percentage point , respectively .
the imf furthermore lower the forecast of next year 's economic growth for a large number of region and country .
accord to its newest estimate , the rate of economic growth of industrialized country this year will be 3.9 % and next year it will be 3.6 % .
among them , america 's rate of economic growth next year will fall from this year 's 3.8 % down to 2.4 % , and japan 's rate of economic growth next year will be only 1.1 % .
the economic growth of such country as korea , thailand , indonesia , malaysia , and the philippines all will clearly slow down .
the imf also make a new forecast for trend in world trade in commodity and labor .
