foreign trade over the year show the follow characteristic :
xinhua news agency , beijing , january 11 th , by reporter kun li and kai li
the economic and trade exchange between the inland and hong kong show a trend of rapid , healthy and steady development in 1997 .
the statistic from china 's custom bureau show that , by november of 1997 , the total volume of import and export between hong kong and the inland be 45.085 billion us dollar , account for 15.7 % of the total volume of import and export of the inland , increase 27 % over the same period last year ; among which export to hong kong by the inland be 38.913 billion us dollar , increase 36.2 % over the same period last year ; and import from hong kong by the inland be 6.172 billion us dollar , decrease 10.7 % over the same period last year .
ministry of foreign trade and economic cooperation official in charge of the economic and trade exchange with hong kong say that , the growth rate of import and export and the growth rate of export to hong kong by the inland be far higher than the growth rate of import and export and the growth rate of export of the inland ( at a rate of 14 % and 23.2 % ) over the same period , and be one of the inland region with the fastest export growth .
at present , hong kong be the second largest trade partner and the largest export market of the inland .
regard investment , hong kong be still the primary source of overseas investment attract by the inland .
from january to september of last year , the inland absorb 6,165 project directly invest by hong kong , account for 40.99 % of the country 's total number over the same period , and the agree value of hong kong capital be 11.711 billion us dollar , account for 33.8 % of the country 's total investment over the same period and the actual value of utilize hong kong capital be 15.418 billion us dollar , account for 48.93 % of the country 's total value over the same period .
regard foreign contracted project and cooperation of labor service , the hong kong region be still the most important market of the inland .
from january to november of last year , the inland sign 1,474 new contract for foreign contract project and cooperation of labor service and design consultation in hong kong , with a contract value of 2.094 billion us dollar , a completed turnover of 1.58 billion us dollar and 21,153 man - time of labor service sent to hong kong .
( end )
xinhua news agency , beijing , jan. 11 th , by reporter yuhong qian
the bank of china , the largest foreign exchange bank in china , have good business performance in 1997 , and realize a profit of 6.033 billion yuan for the whole year , of which domestic bank realize a profit of 2.428 billion yuan .
gross profit continually occupy first place amongst every domestic financial organization .
the bank of china actively and steadily promote various operation system reform such as the credit management system , the audit system and the personnel management system , etc. in 1997 , and also perform exploration in the area of establish market operate mechanism .
regard operation , this bank strengthen deposit work , make rmb deposit growth rate come back , at the same time , through method such as sign bank - enterprise cooperation agreement and strengthen service to major client , etc. , develop potential high grade client .
accord to statistic , the balance of deposit in rmb of bank of china reach 591.239 billion yuan last year , the balance of loan for all item in rmb reach 564.452 billion yuan ; the balance of deposit for foreign currency be 35.508 billion us dollar and the balance of loan for all item with cash foreign exchange be 39.787 billion us dollar .
at the same time , the bank of china have also pay attention to bring all advantage into full play , actively develop the work of market ; make the traditional business of international settlement continue to maintain an advantageous position in furious market competition ; and also gain the new development of intermediate service such as foreign exchange settlement and sale , credit card , agent , substitute charge , etc .
