xinhua news agency , helsinki , january 13 th , by reporter huanqing zheng
accord to the latest statistic data publish by finland custom , in 1997 , finland 's export to southeast asia grow by 28 % .
up till october of last year , finland 's export volume to major trade partner , such as hong kong , china , indonesia , thailand , singapore , malaysia etc. , reach 10.7 billion finland mark ( 1 finland mark approximate 0.19 us dollar ) , which be equivalent to gross export of the whole year of 1996 .
the proportion of finland 's export to this region in its total export increase from 1 % ten year ago to 6.2 % .
the main commodity finland export to this region be mechanical and electronic industry product as well as transport equipment , etc .
at the same time , finland 's import from southeast asia grow by 5 % .
in recently year , finland have be keep an obvious trade surplus in this region .
finland custom estimate that , the financial crisis in southeast asia may weaken finland 's export to this region , in particular , the export of electromechanical product would be impact .
