xinhua news agency , beijing , january 14 th , by reporter zongming zhou
after the successful implementation of a " soft land " , the rumble train of china 's economy be run forward smoothly at high speed .
" proper , quick and stable " growth will become the main theme of this year 's economic development .
official authority reveal that this year the chinese government determine that the economic growth rate be 8 % and price level will be control within 3 % .
this mean that the whole economic operation situation will maintain a healthy pattern of " high growth and low inflation " .
people in economic circle seem to be more optimistic about the economic outlook .
the growth rate , predict by concern expert of the state plan commission , the statistical bureau and the china academy of social science , be mostly 1 to 2 percentage point higher than governmental plan .
of course , to a relatively large extent , this depends on aggregate control of use monetary policy as a primary mean , or in other word , under the major premise of general tighten , how financial control should timely and reasonably conduct fine tune .
moreover , the impact of southeast asia 's financial crisis should not be underestimate .
on the part of the government , the keynote of a moderately tight macro @-@ economic policy will not be change .
the key of the current economy be not strive for a higher growth rate , but be adjust structure and increase benefit so as to make macro control which be implement from the second half year of 1993 obtain greater achievement and push the national economy onto a road of constant , rapid and healthy development .
actually , as main obstacle that restrain economic growth in the past several year -- inflation and the " bottleneck " of basic industry have all be evidently relieve and the macro @-@ economic situation tend to loosen , china 's economic development be in a relatively favorable period .
this year , china plan to create an effective pull force to economic growth through maintain a moderate and stable growth of investment , consumption and export .
fix asset investment will grow by 10 % this year , total volume of retail sale of social consumer product by 10 % and export growth by 8 % .
at the same time , the financial deficit will be reduce by 10 billion yuan .
after bid farewell to the age of " the shortage economy " , relation between commodity 's supply and demand have change from a " buyer ' market " to an integrated " seller ' market " and competition will be intensify .
hence , activate the consumer market , especially the wide rural market , cultivate consumer hotspots and new economic growth point appear to be particularly urgent .
along with comprehensively implement hardship relief measure take towards large and medium - sized state own enterprise , the pace of state own enterprise reform will be accelerate greatly , the dynamic of bankruptcy , merger and asset restructure will be strengthen , and enterprise deficit be estimate to decrease by 20 % and a number of competitive large and medium - sized state own enterprise will gradually form .
however , the large amount of worker layoff that will accompany this will cause unemployment pressure to gradually increase .
china have determine to appropriately place lay - off worker and to strive to control the unemployment rate to within 3.5 % through implementation of a large scale " re @-@ employment " project .
accord to estimate , after three year in a row of bumper harvest , if this year 's measure be effective , agriculture still have hope of achieve a good harvest .
agriculture 's increase production and peasant ' increase revenue will create favorable condition for inhibit commodity price and realize the target of steady economic development .
currently , the degree of dependence on the outside of china 's economy have reach 42 % , and the space of utilize overseas market and resource be in the process of expand , but be more easily subject to the influence of the international environment .
under the circumstance of a relative steady domestic demand , the pull effect of the trend of foreign trade towards economic development be more striking .
take all factor as a whole , this year 's amount of foreign trade will be increase steadily , the import will be increase and the increase speed of the export will be somewhat slow down .
people in economic circle say that china should adopt positive and steady measure to solve outstanding problem in economic operation , and special attention should be give to clear up bad asset in time and strengthen financial risk prevention .
forecast the year of the tiger , although china 's economic train will have up and down , as long as adjust and controlled measure be at the right time and appropriate , it be believe that the train will move steadily along the preset track .
( end )
xinhua news agency , beijing , january 14 th , by reporter yongjian lu
information from the ministry of foreign trade and economic say that , after high - speed development in previous year , china 's foreign investment attract have enter an adjustment period .
statistic figure show that , from january to november in 1997 , the number and contract sum of recently approve foreign investment project decrease by 15.39 % and 33.52 % respectively over the same period last year , the amount of average foreign investment per project decrease 21.33 % over the same period last year , and the proportion of industrial project in recently approve project also decrease by 5.4 % .
since reform and open up to the outside world , china have be promote attract foreign investment even more as an important part of the basic national policy of open up , the past five year have be five year when foreign merchant ' investment grow fastest , and foreign investment have step into the majority of field of china 's national economy .
the amount of foreign investment actually utilize by china have be increase in successive year , create an historical high in 1997 , and a number of project with particularly intensify technology and fund have appear .
on the other hand , since 1994 and 1995 , the number of recently approve foreign investment project and the contract sum have be continually decrease , which will directly affect china 's foreign investment attraction growth rate in the period to come .
expert concern point out that , after high - speed development in previous year , decelerate of the rate of china attract foreign investment be normal .
however , at the begin of this year , concern party announce that , for project that have foreign invest , and which be in field encourage by china such as the new , high technology industry , infrastructure , etc. , the country would implement certain preferential taxation policy .
accord to estimate , these policy would attract more foreign company to invest in china .
