xinhua news agency , beijing , january 3 rd
in order to perfect the management of international commercial loan , the national foreign exchange bureau decide to implement a new method of manage international commercial loan borrow by domestic institution from january 1 st this year .
accord to regulation by the national foreign exchange management bureau , international commercial loan indicate loan raise and borrow by domestic institution from financial institution , enterprise , individual or other economic organization abroad , and from foreign - funded financial institution within china 's border , whose contractual repayment obligation be in foreign currency .
export credit , international finance leaseholds , compensation trade with foreign exchange repayment method , overseas institution 's and individual 's foreign exchange deposit ( exclude foreign exchange deposit in bank approve for offshore operation ) , project finance , finance under trade project over 90 day and other form of foreign exchange loan will all be treat and manage as international commercial loan .
accord to regulation , the people 's bank of china be the approve authority for international commercial loan borrow by domestic institution , the people 's bank of china have authorize the national foreign exchange management bureau to be specifically responsible for the approval , supervision and management of commercial loan by domestic institution .
all international commercial loan borrow by domestic institution should be approve by the national foreign exchange management bureau .
international business loan that have not be approve but be sign on their own authority will not be valid , the foreign exchange management bureau will not process the registration of foreign debt , bank be not allow to open exclusive foreign debt account for them , loan principal and interest be not to be remit out on their own authority .
the national foreign exchange management bureau clearly stipulate in the new method that , domestic institution borrow international commercial loan externally be only limit to : china - capital financial institution approve by the foreign exchange management bureau to operate foreign exchange loan business ; juridical people of non @-@ financial corporation approve by the state department 's authorization department .
juridical people of non @-@ financial institution who borrow international commercial loan directly must possess these several condition , that be , have continual profit for the last three year , have import and export business permission , belong to a national encouraged industry ; possess a complete financial management system ; must have a ratio of net asset to total asset not lower than 15 % for juridical people of trade - type non @-@ financial corporation , must have ratio of net asset to total asset not lower than 30 % for juridical people of non trade - type non @-@ financial corporation ; must have a total sum of international business loan borrow and foreign guarantee surplus not exceed 50 % of net asset 's equivalent foreign exchange worth ; must have total of foreign exchange loan and foreign exchange guarantee surplus not exceed the amount of exchange create in the previous year .
( end )
xinhua news agency , beijing , january 16 , by wire ( reporter wenxin fan )
kazuo nakamura , director of research at japan 's dai - ichi kangyo bank , say here today that the real growth rate of the world economy in 1998 will be about 3 % .
kazuo nakamura , at a public lecture jointly organize by beijing 's wu jia economic consult company , ltd. and japan 's dai - ichi kangyo bank , make a report concern the new year 's world economic and financial situation .
after he review the world economic and financial situation of ' 97 , he say that due to the economic growth in asia , include japan , further slow down , the economic growth of america , even though its current economic activity be relatively good , and of other country will also feel a very large effect .
compare with the rapid growth of the past , the world economy have enter a period of adjustment .
he forecast that the real growth rate for the world economy this year would fall from the 3.9 % of ' 97 down to 3 % .
nakamura think that the rate of economic growth of asia 's country and region , with korea and thailand be the most prominent , would slide downward to a large extent .
but , he say , for these country the currency already have devalue to a great degree , export have recover , and import could decrease .
because of this , he expect that their economy would slip downward to the lowest point in the next half year .
he estimate that the rate of economic growth in asean would be about 4.5 percent .
nakamura say that the japanese economy exhibit negative growth in the year ' 97 , and that in ' 98 , if it do n't adopt good economic policy , the economy would continue to be in negative growth .
he estimate it would be negative 0.5 percent , plus or minus .
he say further that china 's economic growth would also slow in speed , feel the effect of the economy of japan and asia be depress and of the devaluation of these country ' currency .
but because china 's usual income and expenditure show a favorable balance , and in addition it have over 100 billion us dollar in foreign exchange reserve , it be n't likely to sink into the crisis like the other asian nation .
( end )
xinhua news agency , beijing , january 16 th , by reporter xingtang xu and yuhong qian
the president of the people 's bank of china , xianglong dai say , china would continue to implement financial policy open to the outside .
xianglong dai emphasize at the national and foreign reporter news press conference hold today that , china would not give up on financial policy open to the outside because of financial turmoil occur in some country in southeast asia .
he say , another group of foreign bank and insurance company have establish branch institution in china last year , and that by year end , the number of business orient financial institution establish in china with foreign capital have reach more than 170 .
henceforth , the number of branch institution of foreign bank and insurance company in china would also suitably increase , and at the same time would also prepare to expand experimentation of foreign bank handle rmb business .
at the same time , he also emphasize that , henceforth , more careful management of condition of foreign financial institution ' application to operate business in china and qualification of senior staff , and the legality of their business would be implement .
he say , as there never be a schedule for exchangeability under rmb capital project , therefore the process of delay the process due to the southeast asian financial crisis do not exist .
however , in the area of open up capital project , the lesson learn from the financial crisis in southeast asia will be assimilate , and a more careful attitude will be adopt .
