xinhua news agency , shenyang , january 19 th , by reporter jianzhen dong
in liaoning , the old industrial base of china , 21.8 yuan of every 100 yuan of fix asset investment be utilize from foreign capital .
fix asset investment utilize foreign capital have account for more than 1 / 5 of this province 's total fix asset investment .
this be what guozhu gao , provincial vice @-@ governor of liaoning province , mention at the provincial foreign investment utilization work conference hold recently .
during the six year from 1992 to 1997 , foreign investment actually transfer in have approach 13 billion us dollar , account for 21.8 % of the total fix asset investment in the same period .
guozhu gao say : " for liaoning , an old industrial base , which be implement large - scale transformation of the old industrial base , but be also poorly - fund , utilize foreign investment have become one of the main drive force in economic development . "
during the six year , nearly 6000 foreign - invest enterprise have go into operation and production in liaoning , and have accumulatively actualized a production value of nearly 270 billion yuan .
in 1997 , the annual production value of foreign - invest enterprise break through 60 billion yuan , the proportion of annual production value of foreign - invest enterprise in provincial industrial production value have increase from 5 % in 1992 to 17 % .
utilize foreign investment vigorously propel liaoning 's economic development , and promote social stability .
guozhu gao mention that , in 1997 , tax revenue from foreign - invest enterprise in liaoning reach 3 billion yuan , and the proportion account for provincial industrial and commercial tax revenue have rise from 3 % in 1992 to more than 10 % .
out of the operate foreign - invest enterprise in liaoning , the number of directly place employee have reach more than 600,000 , and have become one of the important channel in solve the employment problem .
the area in which liaoning utilize foreign investment have be expand from medium and small - sized process project to the four pillar industry for old industrial base transformation purpose : the petrochemical industry , the metallurgical industry , the mechanical industry , the electronic industry , etc. and such industry as agriculture , real estate , infrastructure , energy , finance , etc .
guozhu gao say : " co @-@ operative area between foreign company and liaoning be still expand constantly . "
method of utilize foreign investment have show a trend of diversified development .
guozhu gao mention that , the shenyang - dalian highway company , ltd. , co @-@ operate with foreign investment , with a total investment of 4.9 billion yuan , have be approve by the ministry of foreign trade and economic cooperation .
china 's largest iron and steel company , the anshan iron and steel corporation , have be list in hong kong for h - share transaction .
the dalian wadian group , have be list for issue b - share , and have raise fund of 390 million us dollar .
liaoning be actively adopt new measure of utilize foreign investment , such as develop the list of new share , property right transfer , asset lease , etc .
