xinhua news agency , washington , january 20 th , by reporter hongqi li
vice @-@ minister of china 's external trade and economic co @-@ operation ministry and concurrent chief negotiation representative yongtu long express in washington on the 20 th that the two country , the us and china , must co @-@ operate closely , in an active and realistic spirit , appropriately manage trade imbalance between the us and china and other trade dispute , to create good external condition for further development of healthy and stable economic and trade relation between the two country .
yongtu long make the above statement during a speech hold by the us - asian foundation .
he say , current world economic globalization be develop deeply , investment flow be faster than trade flow , overseas investment and sale volume of large western country have greatly exceed local import value , the proportion of foreign investment replace direct import be significantly increase .
under these circumstance , use scientific method to implement trade statistic be important , and continue use of traditional trade income and expense balance method to gauge the trade relation between country be already diverge from reality .
during his speech , he quote the conclusion from the latest research report by an american expert group regard the sino - american trade statistic problem .
the report be write by famous expert and scholar from the us 's harvard university and the university of california after nearly six month of research .
it clearly analyzed the sino - american economy and trade relation development situation in 1995 , point out that after exclude various factor such as hong kong 's transfer trade , etc. , the us trade volume with china that year be between 15.6 to 21.6 billion us dollar , drastically lower than the statistical data of 34 billion us dollar announce officially by the us .
at the same time , yongtu long point out that the chinese side understand the concern of the american side over sino - american trade imbalance .
the chinese side will adopt active and practical step to further reduce tariff , reduce non @-@ tariff management measure , improve market entry condition and increase import from the us .
at the same time , the chinese side also hope the american side will relax restriction over the export of chinese high - tech product , gradually jointly realize a trade balance between the two country use positive method , to create condition for the healthy and stable development of sino - american economy and trade relation .
yongtu long come to washington from boston on the 18 th to participate in speech .
he will fly to san francisco on the afternoon of the 20 th to participate in another round of speech .
hawaii will be the last stop of his nine - day us trip .
