accord to presentation , the dependency of china 's export product on the japanese market have be increase annually , but the proportion of import product in the total import volume from japan have fluctuate irregularly ; the development of various trade method be not balance , general trade have decrease , process trade have increase ; while the growth of primary product trade be considerably fast .
