accord to what have be report in the soviet " science and life " magazine , biologist in moscow have discover that a mold element in the cell of plant can not only control the propagation of plasmodium in mosquito , but can also kill mosquito .
this method will not pollute the environment .
biologist mix a mold element in the cell of plant with pearl powder to produce a granulate drug .
this kind of drug can slowly discharge the mold element from the cell of plant in water .
when mosquito fee , they suck the mold element from the cell of plant into their body .
experiment have show that adopt this method can reduce the chance of mosquito transmit malaria down to 1 @/@ 70 th to 1 @/@ 80 th of the original ratio .
