xinhua news agency , moscow , august 31 st , by reporter rong xie
due to the report failure of all effort of the heavy - duty transport spaceship " progress m - 24 " , which be deliver cargo to " peace " , to dock with the orbital station , the food on the " peace " orbital station , which lack supply , be only enough for the three russian astronaut work on the orbital station to last for 10 day before the routine scientific research work of the astronaut would be affect .
the international information telegraph agency report that the heavy - duty transport spaceship " progress m - 24 " be send into outer space from the baikonur spaceship launch site on august 25 .
carry aboard be 639 kilogram of such article as food , water , fuel , scientific instrument , etc .
by design , the heavy - duty spaceship " progress m - 24 " , in unman operate mode , can perform automate dock with the orbital station .
but on the 27 th , the first attempt of the spaceship to dock with the orbital station fail .
on the 30 th , the spaceship attempt to dock with the orbital station again , and the second dock fail again .
today , the technology committee of russian space - flight control center hold a meet to analyze the reason for the two fail dockings and decide to perform a third dock attempt on september 2 nd .
this time will employ manual control method by the astronaut work in the orbital station to achieve dock from the orbital station .
this will be the last chance for this cargo spaceship to dock with the orbital station because the fuel on the spaceship be already very limit .
if it fail , a new cargo spaceship must be launch to transport cargo to the orbital station .
also , the russian correspondence agency - tass report that the inter @-@ department committee of the russian space orbital station operation will also convene a meet today to research countermeasure .
ivanov , chairman of this committee and commander of russian military space force , say that the third dock will be complete successfully because space expert on the ground have put out all effort for this .
austelouwumuff , vice @-@ bureau chief of russian space bureau also point out that all work be currently be carry out normally .
he deny the statement that the food reserve on the orbital station be only enough to last 10 day .
he say that the food on the " peace " orbital station could still meet need for 40 day .
moreover , even if the third dock fail , a new cargo spaceship can still be launch to transport material .
