the direct hit by typhoon no. 17 damage 862 kilometers of the dike in wenzhou , of which , up to 357.7 kilometers be completely wash away .
while the big tide on august 3 rd and august 15 th of the lunar calendar approach again before your eye , new typhoon and rain storm may come at any time , make one worry about the danger .
the people of wenzhou be now urgently take action , deal with the emergency , rebuild the dike and protect their home .
