xinhua news agency , zhengzhou , april 23 rd , by reporter yaming liu
recently , relate expert and scholar discover a large quantity of dinosaur bone fossil in yangcheng township , xixia county of henan province .
this be another big discovery come after an abundance of precious dinosaur egg fossil be discover here at the begin of last year .
this reporter have learn from the archaeological institute of cultural relic that at the begin of april of this year , relate expert discover several hundred dinosaur bone fossil , include rib , phalanges , etc. , between two river gravel layer at such place as hutou hill , yangcheng township , xixia county , etc .
because of long - term exposure at the ground 's surface , some be already break .
from the view of stratigraphy , they all belong to the cretaceous period .
accord to expert ' judgment , a large quantity of dinosaur fossil and other species ' fossil be still bury within the dinosaur fossil group distribution area .
they believe that the discovery of a large quantity of valuable dinosaur egg fossil in the xixia basin be an international rarity , and egg fossil and bone fossil exist in one place be even rarer .
this find be of great important significance for study dinosaur classification in the xixia area , probe into dinosaur zoology and breed habit , restore the zoology and ecology of the dinosaur era and reveal law about the earth 's surface change and the earth 's environment evolve .
the discovery of the dinosaur bone fossil also provide important clue about the region and burial pattern for further search for dinosaur fossil .
