xinhua news agency , nanjing , september 1 st , by reporter yanghe yuan
professor yuyi liu , a painter whose famous canvas " a happy night " cause a sensation in the art world , recently in nanjing make public a yuhua stone he have discover - " the stone of the divine land with five unique feature " .
the appearance and size of this yuhua stone be quite similar to an auspicious folk object , a longevity locket .
in the very middle of the yuhua stone be a clear image of the territory of the people 's republic of china .
the image , with its two end tower , a sunken middle section , and the lower right part protrude , look like a rooster crane and crow with its neck stretch and chest thrown out ; on the side of the " rooster 's " belly be the long and narrow " taiwan island " , which be separate by " strait " ; under the claw of the " rooster " be the round " hainan island " .
the color and luster of the two " island " be completely the same as the " mainland " .
the whole image be almost the same as the map of china .
professor yuyi liu say that he pick up the stone on the road to a yuhua stone process plant in a suburb of nanjing five year ago , and after he return home he carefully inspect the stone and discover the " territory of china " on it .
at the same time he also discover that entrench above the mainland territory and along the frontier line of the northeast , the north , and the northwest of china be a huge dragon with a bright pearl in its mouth ; above this huge dragon , there be a golden facula in the shape of a gold dollar ; in the middle of the mainland territory , there be a string of torch - shape stripe symbolize the eternal flame of life of the chinese nation ; add in its resemblance to a longevity locket , altogether this stone have 5 special feature .
accord to this , yuyi liu name this stone " the stone of the divine land with five unique feature " .
( end )
xinhua news agency , hanoi , april 23 rd , by reporter shuojing hu
six country , namely china , thailand , vietnam , burma , laos and cambodia , will further strengthen co @-@ operation in such area as transportation , energy , trade and investment , environmental protection , tourism and human resource development , etc .
this be the common understand held by representative of the six aforementioned country at the asian development bank 's third secondary region economic co @-@ operation meet , which close today .
this meet also decide that transportation be content that be focal to secondary region co @-@ operation .
the two highway from kunming to chiang mai , thailand and from kunming to lashio , burma , and the two railroad from yunnan to vietnam , and from yunnan to thailand be list as the project take first priority in be develop .
this meet be organize by the vietnamese government and asian development bank .
the meet be chair by government delegation of the 6 aforementioned country and representative of some international organization and institute .
in 1992 , the asian development bank first propose various aspect of economic co @-@ operation within the secondary region form by china ( yunnan ) , cambodia , laos , burma , thailand and vietnam , and also decide a number of co @-@ operation and development project of regional significance .
the first and second asian development bank 's secondary region economic co @-@ operation meeting be hold in manila in october , 1992 and in august , 1993 .
( end )
xinhua news agency , hanoi , august 31 st , by reporter shuojing hu
at a press conference hold here today , samuel insanally , chairman of the un assembly , appeal to the international community to further assist vietnam to recover and develop its economy .
insanally emphasize that help vietnam to recover production and construction be the international community 's current responsibility .
he appeal to country participate in the " parisian international meet on assist vietnam " to be hold in paris in november of this year to extend economic aid to vietnam .
at the " parisian international meet on assist vietnam " hold in november of last year , vietnam totally receive aid of 1.86 billion us dollar from such country as japan , france , korea , sweden , etc .
insanally also express that the un will strengthen its assistance program to vietnam .
currently , the un development and plan office alone have implement nearly 300 large and small development project in vietnam , with a worth of over 400 million us dollar .
insanally arrive in hanoi on the 28 th for a 4 - day visit on the invitation of mengqin run , foreign minister of vietnam .
( end )
xinhua news agency , jerusalem , august 31 st , by reporter chengbo huai
today , the " jerusalem post " quote the word of shawel , director of the administrative office of the israeli foreign ministry who be now visit the us as say that the world bank have decide to provide 250 million us dollar of aid to palestinian autonomous authority before the end of 1994 .
this decision broke the impasse between donor country and palestinian autonomous authority that have last for nearly one year .
at the international meet on aid palestinian autonomy which be hold in washington on october 1 st of last year , donor country pledge to provide 2.4 billion us dollar of development aid within 5 year , of which 750 million us dollar would be appropriate in the first year .
but donor country claim that the palestinian autonomous region lack necessary mechanism for handle the aid and account item and therefore refuse to completely fulfill this promise .
shawel say that although the us and the world bank be currently not completely satisfy with palestinian account work , they have still agree to pay a portion of the fund as soon as possible .
arafat , chairman of the executive committee of the palestinian liberation organization , and other palestinian leader have be criticize the donor country for not be able to keep their promise to make sure the money aid be completely in place and on time .
it be predict that shashe , the plo 's chief negotiation representative , and rosechird , israel 's chief negotiation representative , will go to washington to specifically negotiate and determine the aid issue with the us and the world bank .
( end )
xinhua news agency , beijing , september 1 st , by reporter jianxin gao
in order to strengthen cultural exchange and contact between the descendents of the emperor at home and abroad , china will hold the " china art festival " in beijing and shenzhen simultaneously from the 8 th to the 18 th of december this year .
this will be a grand art meet jointly hold by the people 's organization , government cultural department and enterprise .
its aim be to use chinese national traditional culture as a link to associate and unite compatriot at home and abroad , to spread national culture , to display the charm of the superior art of the motherland and display the achievement and elegant demeanor of overseas chinese , chinese artist in art realm and international cultural exchange .
the art festival mainly include a grand open ceremony and closing ceremony , large scale theatrical performance with various characteristic , and painting and photographic exhibition .
accord to presentation , the art festival to open at the shenzhen gymnasium on december 8 th will focus on display the most widely circulate chinese artistic extract of the 20 th century .
start from december 9 th , every night , at either shenzhen 's great theater or the shenzhen gymnasium , a high level program will be stage , and programs such as ballet , stand - up comedy , highlight from beijing opera and overseas chinese artist and artistic troupe , etc. will be separately perform .
during the art festival , a competition for the award of traditional paint and copy , an exhibition of work , and an international " light of china " exhibition of photographic art of overseas chinese and chinese will be hold in beijing .
this art festival be jointly hold by work unit such as the chinese national federation of return overseas chinese , the ministry of culture , cctv , the cultural department of shenzhen city , the overseas chinese international cultural exchange promotion association of china , etc .
( end )
xinhua news agency , beijing , april 23 rd
zemin jiang , president of the people 's republic of china , and peng li , premier of the state council , send a telegraph of condolence on the 23 rd on the pass of former us president , richard nixon .
the full telegraphic text be as follow :
shock by the unfortunate pass of mr. richard nixon due to illness , we hereby express heartfelt condolence .
mr. nixon be a politician possess strategic foresight and political courage .
during his tenure as us president , he open up the door of sino - american relation together with the late chairman zedong mao and premier enlai zhou , create a new phase in the two country ' relation .
after resign , mr. nixon continue to be concern about sino - american relation , and have make important contribution to the maintenance and development of the two country ' relation .
we deeply believe that with the mutual effort of both china and the us , the sino - american relation which mr. nixon be very concern with during his lifetime will definitely see further improvement and development .
we express our sincere solicitude for the family member of mr. nixon .
( end )
xinhua news agency , canberra , august 31 st
the chinese government and the australian government sign an agreement today , wherein the australian party would provide china with a preferential financial loan of 150 million australian dollar .
accord to the agreement , this loan will be mainly use in infrastructure project such as telecommunications , municipal water supply and sewage treatment , etc .
last for two day , the ' 94 development assistance cooperation annual meet between the chinese government and the australian government conclude today in melbourne .
the chinese delegation with yongtu long , assistant minister of the ministry of foreign economy and trade , as the delegation leader , and the australian delegation with flad , director general of australian international development bureau assistance department as the delegation leader , chair the meet .
after the talk be over , the two party sign the summary of the talk .
at the same time , the australia side will provide china with a technical cooperation grant of 20 million australian dollar , which will be mainly use in project such as personnel train , support the poor , medical treatment , sanitation , etc .
( end )
xinhua news agency , beijing , september 1 st
this afternoon at the great people 's hall , chairman of the stand committee of the npc , shi qiao , meet with a russian parliamentary group lead by vice chairman wenkerlorphsky of the national duma and vice chairman sharegernkerf of the russian federation economic reform committee .
the representative group come on august 30 th to china on the invitation of the foreign affair institute , aim at understand the situation of economic reform in china , the protective role of economic legislation during the process of build up a market economy structure , especially successful experience in the area of special economic zone construction .
in the even , president of the foreign affair institute , shuqin liu , meet with and invite the russian guest to a banquet .
( end )
xinhua news agency , beijing , august 31 st
premier peng li deliver a write speech to welcome the international population and development congress .
he think that the chinese government 's guidelines of plan , strategizing and implementation of the population problem and socioeconomic problem as one be correct , effective in its implementation , and successful .
peng li say that in the begin of september of this year , the unite nation would hold the international population and development congress in cairo with the theme of " population , continuous economic growth and continuous development " .
this show that the international community have increasingly recognize that population and development be inseparable , and prepare to adopt action together .
he feel that this congress have important mean , and the chinese government have give it high level attention and will be send a delegation to attend the congress .
peng li say china be the most populous develop country in the world .
the chinese government include the population problem into the overall plan of the national economy and its social development , always emphasize that population growth and economic development need to fit together , and be coordinated with resource utilization and environmental protection .
in light of china 's basic national condition , the chinese government have determine plan parenthood and environmental protection as two basic national policy , implement a population policy and plan parenthood program that suit china 's actual need .
at the same time , the chinese government also formulate a series of important policy and measure to realize continuous development , such as the protection of women 's legal right and benefit , the promotion of equality among men and women , the forceful development of healthcare for women and children , the zealous elimination of poverty , and protect the environment .
presently , the chinese economy be continuously grow , society be stable and unite , people 's livelihood be continuously improve , and the population birth rate and the natural population growth rate have drop to a lower level .
peng li say the population problem be one of the major problem currently face by the international community .
due to difference in country 's situation , difference in economic development level , cultural background , historical tradition , and social system , each country should formulate suitable , effective population policy accord to the actual situation of the native country .
this be the sovereignty of each country and it should receive full respect .
he say china be in a critical period of build up a socialist market economy system and increase the pace of its modernization build - up , but a huge , overwhelm growth in population be still restrain the social and economic development , affect the further improvement of the live standard of the people , and have also bring about heavy pressure on the natural resource and the natural environment .
because of this , for a fairly long period of time , at the same time as forcefully develop the economy , china will continue to pay close attention to do well the work of family plan .
the chinese government strongly believe that , the resolution of china 's population problem be not just be responsible for the prosperity of the chinese race and the happiness of future generation , but be also an important contribution in stabilize the world 's population .
for this , the chinese government view with extreme importance and actively participate in international population activity , and sincerely hope that the international community will adopt a stand of realistic resolution of population and development problem , seek similarity while accommodate difference , co @-@ operate closely to strive hard together towards a stable world population to create a beautiful future !
